NK129(to)002:1: // dpal rdo rje phur pa'i lo rgyus chos kyi 'byung
NK129(to)002:2: gnas ngo mtshar rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs zhes bya ba'i
NK129(to)002:4: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i lo rgyus ngo mtshar rgya
NK129(to)002:5: mtsho'i rba rlabs zhes bya ba bla ma dang dpal
NK129(to)002:6: rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK129(to)002:7: rig 'dzin bla ma rgyal ba sras dang bcas //
NK129(to)002:8: yi dam lha dang mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho la //
NK129(to)002:9: bdag yid gus pas rtag par phyag bgyis te //
NK129(to)002:10: yang gsang chos kyi gtam brgyus bsgrags par bya //
NK129(to)002:11: de la ston pa phun sum tshogs pa dang po'i
NK129(to)002:12: sangs rgyas kun tu bzang pos dus phun sum tshogs
NK129(to)002:13: pa dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dus //
NK129(to)002:14: gnas phun sum tshogs pa 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi zhing khams su /
NK129(to)002:15: skye med mtha' bral chen po'i dgongs pa las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK129(to)002:16: 'gag med cho 'phrul bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK129(to)002:17: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum du sku bzhengs te
NK129(to)002:18: thabs shes rab gnyis su med par sbyor ba las
NK129(to)002:19: / 'khor phun sum tshogs pa phyogs bcu'i khro bo phra thabs dang /
NK129(to)002:20: phur pa sras kyi 'khor mngon par sprul nas /
NK129(to)002:21: chos phun sum tshogs pa byi to ta ma la 'bum sde la sogs pa /
NK129(to)002:22: 'phrin las phur pa'i rgyud mtha' dag gsungs so //
NK129(to)002:28: bram ze mi'i thod pa can la sogs pas yang dag par bsdus so //
NK129(to)002:29: ci 'khor gyis bsdus pa nyid rigs kyi /
NK129(to)002:30: ston pa nyid kyis bsdus pa mi 'thad do snyam na /
NK129(to)002:31: de ni 'di skad bdag gis bshad pa'i dus gcig na /
NK129(to)002:32: ces pa dang gsang dus kyi slob dpon mtsho skyes
NK129(to)002:33: rdo rje mdzad pa'i gsang ba grub pa las 'brel
NK129(to)002:34: ba las / slob dpon kha cig 'di skad du /
NK129(to)002:35: dpal ldan 'dus pa mdangs can gyis //
NK129(to)002:36: rgyud kyi bsdud par byed pa po //
NK129(to)002:37: dpal bo 'jig rten dbang phyug zer //
NK129(to)002:38: bla ma'i zhabs kyi bka' drin gyis //
NK129(to)002:39: dpal ldan 'dus pa'i bsdud pa po //
NK129(to)002:40: gzhan dag yod pa ma yin zhes //
NK129(to)002:41: bdag nyid 'ba' zhig smra bar byed //
NK129(to)002:42: rgyud mdzad pa po ni thugs rdo rje /
NK129(to)002:43: zhes rgya 'brel las 'byung bas gsal ba yin no //
NK129(to)002:44: de nas mkha' 'gro ma dang mi'i yul du rim gyis dar ba yin te /
NK129(to)002:45: ston pa kun tu bzang pos /
NK129(to)002:49: de dag ni rgyal rigs bzhi /
NK129(to)002:50: de dag la slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis gsan no //
NK129(to)002:52: des dga' rab rdo rje la bshad /
NK129(to)002:53: des rgyal po u ru sha ne la /
NK129(to)002:54: des klu'i bu mo rgya mtsho la /
NK129(to)002:55: des rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti la /
NK129(to)002:56: des slob dpon d+ha na sang tri ta /
NK129(to)002:58: blo ldan mchog srid gsum la bshad /
NK129(to)002:62: bal po sh+ai la many+dzu gsum la bshad do //
NK129(to)002:64: rgyal po dza la glegs bam gyi char dngos grub tu phab pa las brgyud pa yang yod te /
NK129(to)002:66: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK129(to)002:67: lo ni brgya dang bcu gnyis na //
NK129(to)002:68: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK129(to)002:69: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK129(to)002:70: spo ti glegs bam snang bar byed //
NK129(to)002:72: rgyal po dza lha lcam go ma de w+ai /
NK129(to)002:73: rgyal bu sha kra pu ri nas rim par brgyud de rgya bal bod du dar ro //
NK129(to)002:74: yang kun tu bzang pos rdo rje gzhon nu la /
NK129(to)002:75: des bram ze mi thod can /
NK129(to)002:76: des mkha' 'gro ma las kyi dbang mo che la gtad /
NK129(to)002:77: des mchod rten bde byed rtsegs par gter du sbas /
NK129(to)002:79: des za hor gyi mkhan po pra hasti /
NK129(to)002:80: des lha lcam u pa d+aa na /
NK129(to)002:81: des slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la brgyud /
NK129(to)002:83: brgyud tshul gzhan yang mang du yod mod kyi /
NK129(to)002:84: 'dir ni bdag cag lta bu mthong ba chung ba
NK129(to)002:85: dag gis ji ltar thos pa nyid bris pa tsam
NK129(to)002:86: mo // da ni sangs rgyas gnyis pa mi yul
NK129(to)002:87: du byon pa slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas zhes bya
NK129(to)002:88: ba 'di'i sku che ba'i tshul mdo tsam smos na
NK129(to)002:89: mo // / 'jam dpal rgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK129(to)002:90: dpal ldan sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes //
NK129(to)002:91: kun mkhyen ye shes mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK129(to)002:93: che ba sangs rgyas rigs sngags rgyal //
NK129(to)002:95: brjod bya bshad thabs phyogs gcig gis chos dang gang
NK129(to)002:96: zag gnyis ga lung bstan pa ltar du spyir slob
NK129(to)002:97: dpon chen po 'di pad+ma la rdzus te skyes pa
NK129(to)002:98: yin na yang / phrin las phur pa'i chos 'di
NK129(to)002:99: spel pa'i slad du mngal du skye ba bzung bar
NK129(to)002:101: de'i rgyu mtshan mngal skyes kyi sems can rnams rdzus skyes kyi mi thul bas /
NK129(to)002:102: sangs rgyas rnams kyang mngal 'dzin pa'i tshul ston dgos pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)002:103: slob dpon gyis kyang mngal du zhugs pa'i tshul bstan pas /
NK129(to)002:104: rgya bod gnyis su slob dpon gyi chos gzhan pas
NK129(to)002:105: phur pa dar che zhing 'di'i sgo nas grol ba
NK129(to)002:106: thob pa dang / grub pa brnyes pa byon pa'i
NK129(to)002:107: rnam grangs brjod kyi mi langs pa'i rgyu mtshan de
NK129(to)002:108: thob pa dang / yin no // de yang o
NK129(to)002:109: rgyan gyi yul na srid skyongs pa'i rgyal po ma
NK129(to)002:110: nu si ta bya ba'i bu d+aa na rak+shi ta
NK129(to)002:111: thob pa dang / yin no // zhes kyang bya
NK129(to)002:112: / sh+aan+ta rak+sha'i ta bya ba kha dog dkar la
NK129(to)002:113: dmar ba'i mdangs dang ldan pas pad+ma'i rigs kyi mtshan
NK129(to)002:114: thob pa dang / yin no // zhes kyang bya
NK129(to)002:115: / dang ldan zhing / rgyu rtsal thams cad rdzogs
NK129(to)002:116: pa mgo dang rked pa rgya mdud ro stod chums
NK129(to)002:117: thob pa dang / yin no // zhes kyang bya
NK129(to)002:118: / dang ldan zhing / bzhogs / ro smad zur
NK129(to)002:119: thob pa dang / yin no // zhes kyang bya
NK129(to)002:120: / dang ldan zhing / bzhogs / gsum / kha
NK129(to)002:121: dang mig zla gam skra kham pa ste /
NK129(to)002:122: mi gdug ba phur pa'i mtshan nyid can zhig skyes so //
NK129(to)002:124: yul de'i rgyal po sras kyis 'phongs pa zhig la /
NK129(to)002:125: nam zhig na sras gcig byung nas /
NK129(to)002:126: de skyed mos tshal du bza' shing gi sil grib
NK129(to)002:127: la brnyal ba'i mgo la sha sbrang cig gis za
NK129(to)002:129: d+aa rak+shi tas rgyal bu shi yi dogs /
NK129(to)002:131: rde'u dang sha sbrang sbrags te klad pa la song nas rgyal bu shi'o //
NK129(to)002:132: 'di la kha cig blon po'i bu tri shu la phog nas bsad zer te /
NK129(to)002:133: rdzus skyes kyi lo rgyus su de ltar yin gyi /
NK129(to)002:136: khyod kyis rgyal bu bsad do byas pas /
NK129(to)002:137: bdag gi ngan sems kyis ma brgyab ste /
NK129(to)002:138: rgyal bu'i mgo la sha sbrang cig za zhing mchis pas /
NK129(to)002:139: sha sbrang la 'phangs pas sor rdo dang bcas pa klad par song nas gum mo //
NK129(to)002:143: rgyal khrims mnyan pas nyes pa rab gsod /
NK129(to)002:145: tha ma lo gsar lhag sgang la nang ma re
NK129(to)002:146: bag phye khal brgya pa re 'jal du 'jug pa
NK129(to)002:147: las / 'di da res rgyal po'i sras bsad pa
NK129(to)002:148: yin pas nyes pa rab tu 'ong steng na sems
NK129(to)002:152: der mda' lnga dang gzhu thogs nas rgya gar gyi dur khrod so sha gling du byon /
NK129(to)002:153: yo byad gzhan ci yang med pas /
NK129(to)002:154: ro zas 'bras chen zas su bza' shing ro ras gos su gyon /
NK129(to)002:155: pho byung tshad btags shing btang /
NK129(to)002:156: mo byung tshad spyad cing btag bas dur khrod na srin po sh+aan+ta rak+shi ta bya ba snang ngo //
NK129(to)002:157: zhes grong khyer kun du gleng ngo //
NK129(to)002:158: de'i tshe yul de'i rgyal po 'thab par dga' ba zhes bya ba khros te /
NK129(to)002:159: 'di ma bsad na yul khams phung ste 'gro bas sod cig ces dgos nas dmag bcas te /
NK129(to)002:160: rgyal po'i bu in+t+ra r+aa dza dpa' zhing brtul bas
NK129(to)002:161: lungs pa'i ngogs dur khrod mdo 'gag dam par dgag
NK129(to)002:162: tu bcug / rgyal po dmag dang bcas pas ri rong dur khrod kun bshus pas /
NK129(to)002:163: sh+aan+ta rak+shi tas bros pa dang /
NK129(to)002:164: dur khrod kyi mdo 'gag na rgyal bu in+t+ra r+aa
NK129(to)002:165: dzas dgug pa dang phrad de der shan+da rak+shi tas
NK129(to)002:166: mda' 'phangs pas / in+t+ra r+aa dza'i snying la phog ste bsad do //
NK129(to)002:167: des bros te song pa na /
NK129(to)002:168: re zhig na lam du mi gnyis dang phrad nas /
NK129(to)002:170: za hor gyi mkhan po la chos nyan par 'gro zer /
NK129(to)002:171: der sngar gyi rang gi spyad pa la skyo ste grogs dang bsdongs te chos la phyin pas /
NK129(to)002:172: lam du slob dpon sh+aakya bo d+hi dang mjal nas gsum ka rab tu byung /
NK129(to)002:173: dge tshul gyi khrims nos te /
NK129(to)002:177: de nas za hor du byon pas /
NK129(to)002:178: slob dpon pra ha ti dang mjal /
NK129(to)002:179: grogs gnyis kyi gser gyis man+dala phul nas chos zhus
NK129(to)002:180: pas gsum ga la yo ga'i dbang rdzogs par bskur
NK129(to)002:181: / gsang mtshan las kyi rdo rje /
NK129(to)002:183: sh+aakya seng ge'i mtshan sems dpa'i rdo zhes btags so //
NK129(to)002:184: ta th+aa sam gra ha'i rgyud mtshan nyid sde gsum ltar bshad nas tshim mam gsungs pas /
NK129(to)002:185: sh+aakya pra b+ha tshim zer nas song /
NK129(to)002:186: gnyis pas ma tshim byas pas sngags phyi pa sde gsum ltar tshar gcig bshad nas tshim mam gsungs /
NK129(to)002:187: sh+aakya mi tra tshim zer nas song /
NK129(to)002:188: sh+aakya seng ges mi bsad pas yul du 'gro sa med pas ma tshim byas pas /
NK129(to)002:189: slob dpon gyis lag mthil du yo ga'i lha rnams gsal bar bstan nas /
NK129(to)002:192: der slob dpon la zhu byas pas /
NK129(to)002:194: rig dbang rig pa'i sras yin pas //
NK129(to)002:195: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor nga las sprul //
NK129(to)002:196: nga ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK129(to)002:197: nga las thams cad byung bas na /
NK129(to)002:198: nga yis bstan pa bzhin du nyon //
NK129(to)002:199: zhes gsungs nas yo ga'i chos thams cad rdzogs par bslab /
NK129(to)002:200: de nas gsang ba bla na med pa sgyu 'phrul gyi dbang rdzogs par bskur /
NK129(to)002:201: de nas phur pa 'bum sde'i chos thams cad rdzogs par bshad pa yin no //
NK129(to)002:202: de nas gnyis su med pa'i ye shes rtogs /
NK129(to)002:203: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob /
NK129(to)002:204: za hor rgyal po'i bu mo me tog man d+aa ra bya ba sgrub byar dkug nas /
NK129(to)002:205: nub phyogs kyi ri bo go ma ha ti sha
NK129(to)002:206: ga'i brag phug ma ra ti ka ru sgrubs par
NK129(to)002:207: rnam pas smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob bo //
NK129(to)002:208: de nas bsad pas mi 'jigs snyam ste /
NK129(to)002:210: sngon rgyal bu in+t+ra r+aa dza bsad pa'i mi thong po yin pa ngo shes nas /
NK129(to)002:212: slob dpon lha lcam dang bcas pa tsan dan gyi me la bsregs te /
NK129(to)002:213: zhag bdun nas du ba chad pa dang bltas pas /
NK129(to)002:214: matshe'u'i dbus na pad+ma'i sdong po gyes pa la slob
NK129(to)002:215: dpon lha lcam gnyis bzhugs pa mthong nas ngo mtshar
NK129(to)002:217: mchod gnas su bzhugs par zhus pas gnang ste /
NK129(to)002:218: rgya gar du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rgyas par gyis cig /
NK129(to)002:219: de ltar ma byas na khyed cag nyams par 'gyur re gsungs nas o rgyan du byon no //
NK129(to)002:220: der yang sngon gyi mi thong po byung ngo zer
NK129(to)002:221: nas yul gyi mi res shing khu re bsdus nas
NK129(to)002:222: me dpung chen po'i dbus su sregs pas ma tshig
NK129(to)002:223: ste / sngar bzhin matshe'u'i dkyil nas pad+ma'i sdong po
NK129(to)002:224: skyes pa'i lte bar bzhugs pa mthong nas thams cad
NK129(to)002:225: ngo mtshar zhing dad pa skyes /
NK129(to)002:226: sngar gyi nyes pa bshags nas /
NK129(to)002:227: o rgyan gyi yul du chos kyi bstan pa brgyas par mdzad do //
NK129(to)002:228: de nas slob dpon gyi dgongs pa la /
NK129(to)002:229: skye shi 'khor ba'i chos dang ni bral /
NK129(to)002:230: mi brjed pa'i gzungs ni thob /
NK129(to)002:232: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin ni brnyes /
NK129(to)002:233: da phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin cig sgrub dgos par dgongs nas /
NK129(to)002:235: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu yang dag mar me dgu pa'i sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:236: yul de'i klu gyong po zhes bya ba dang /
NK129(to)002:237: lha 'dre yongs kyi bar chad byas te /
NK129(to)002:238: lo gsum du gnam las char ma babs /
NK129(to)002:239: sa la rtsi shing nags tshal dang lo thog thams cad bskams /
NK129(to)002:240: chu bo dang chu bran kun kyang rgyun chad te
NK129(to)002:241: dus ngan byung ba'i tshe slob dpon gyi dgongs pa
NK129(to)002:242: la / 'di ni cis kyang ma lan te /
NK129(to)002:243: bdag byang chub sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa zhig go snyam nas /
NK129(to)002:245: lha la gsol ba btab pas /
NK129(to)002:246: nam mkha' las sgra byung ste /
NK129(to)002:247: bar chod 'di gzhan gyis 'dul ba'i thabs med kyis /
NK129(to)002:248: rgya gar sh+ai len+t+ra'i gtsug lag khang nas rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud sde spyan drangs cig /
NK129(to)002:251: gnyis la gser bre gang bkur nas /
NK129(to)002:252: pan+di ta lnga brgya la phul /
NK129(to)002:253: lo rgyus gsol bas rdo rje phur ba'i chos bskor 'bum sde rtsam cig bzhugs pa'i nang nas /
NK129(to)002:254: spo sti mi khur gnyis pan+dita rnams kyis bardzangasa so //
NK129(to)002:255: de yang le shod du sleb pa tsam gyis lha
NK129(to)002:256: 'dre'i bar chad rang sar zhi ste dus kyi 'brug
NK129(to)002:259: rtsi shing nags tshal lo thog thams cad phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)002:260: de tsa na phur pa'i chos 'di bkra shis shing
NK129(to)002:261: byin rlabs myur bas phyogs thams cad du rgyas par
NK129(to)002:263: rgyud sde rnams kyi dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos /
NK129(to)002:265: bsgom pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK129(to)002:266: 'phrin las rdo rje gzhon nu bdab pa las kha tshar dang bzhi ru phye ste mdzad /
NK129(to)002:267: dus der slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK129(to)002:268: bi ma la mu tra dang /
NK129(to)002:269: bal po shi la man+dzu gsum gyis yang le shod du sgrubs pas rtags thon te /
NK129(to)002:271: dus der lung tshad du phyin nam ma phyin dgongs pa mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:272: rtags mngon sum du gzigs pa dang /
NK129(to)002:273: phur smad nyi shu ru bsdus te /
NK129(to)002:275: lung k+ai la ya bcu gnyis kyi tan+t+ra /
NK129(to)002:284: ye shes nyi zer nam mkha' rol pa'i rgyal po'o //
NK129(to)002:297: de tsa na lha bdud du sprul nas drod nyul ba ni /
NK129(to)002:298: lcags kyi sdig pa nag po 'jigs su rung pa
NK129(to)002:299: cig thog babs su mtho mtshams su byung ba la
NK129(to)002:300: slob dpon nyid phag tu bardzusa nas zos par chas
NK129(to)002:301: pas / sdig pa de bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu ri rab brjid pa'i skur mthong /
NK129(to)002:302: drag shul gyi las la thog pa med pa'i dbang thob ste /
NK129(to)002:303: de'i dus su bsnyen phur bsgril shing nga btsan gyi mgur bzhes pa ni /
NK129(to)002:304: ri sta tsakra phur pa'i lha //
NK129(to)002:305: mthing nag gcer bu ral ka can //
NK129(to)002:306: sku stod khro bo chen po la //
NK129(to)002:307: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK129(to)002:308: lte ba man chad phur pa'i dbal //
NK129(to)002:309: drag por gyur pa'i phur pa ste //
NK129(to)002:312: btab na lha yang brlag 'gyur na //
NK129(to)002:313: gnod byed rnams la smos ci dgos //
NK129(to)002:315: de nas bstan bcos rnams pan+di ta lnga brgya la gzigs 'bul bar chas te /
NK129(to)002:316: rgya bal gnyis kyi so mtshams /
NK129(to)002:317: chu mig byang chub tis su gzims pa na rnal lam du sku 'grong ba snyams byung ba dang /
NK129(to)002:319: thugs kha nas sems can gyi dngos po cig zin te spar bur bcug /
NK129(to)002:320: phyag mtshan rdo rje brgyas btab nas bzhag /
NK129(to)002:322: bu mo mtshan sdug dang ldan pa bzhi 'dug ste /
NK129(to)002:325: sngon bcom ldan 'das dpal chen pos dregs pa pho
NK129(to)002:326: bsgral mo sbyor ba'i dus na dam la btags te
NK129(to)002:327: / 'gro ba'i srog la dbang bskur ba'i ma mo bzhi lags te /
NK129(to)002:328: de'i thugs dam gyi dbang gis 'dir 'ongs pa lags kyis /
NK129(to)002:329: slob dpon gyis kyang dbang bskur na 'gro ba thams cad bsod snyam nas /
NK129(to)002:330: rdo rje phur pa nyan pa'i /
NK129(to)002:332: bsgom sgrub byed pa la bar du gcod pa'i srog la dbang gis cig gsungs nas /
NK129(to)002:333: bse mo bzhi dang bka' bsgros nas /
NK129(to)002:334: bse lung tsha ba'i yang gter mdzad de /
NK129(to)002:335: de ltar snga 'gyur gyi phur smad nyi shu rtsa gcig bsnams te /
NK129(to)002:336: shi len+t+ra'i gtsug lag khang du byon nas pan+di ta lnga brgya'i spyan sngar grims pas /
NK129(to)002:337: chos shin tu legs pas rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags /
NK129(to)002:338: pan+di ta rnams kyis kyang slob dpon la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK129(to)002:339: de nas mkhas pa rnam pa gsum gyi bka' bsgros te /
NK129(to)002:340: byi to ta ma la 'bum sde thams cad gzigs te /
NK129(to)002:341: rdo rje phur pa gsang ba'i rgyud la sogs pa
NK129(to)002:342: rgyud sde sum bcu rtsa gnyis la 'brel pa bsgrub
NK129(to)002:343: thabs t+aak+ki la sogs pa phye nas rgyas par mdzad
NK129(to)002:344: de / de'i dus su srod la shwa na ma mched bzhis srog snying phul lo //
NK129(to)002:345: nam gung la bdag nyid ma che bzhis srog snying phul lo //
NK129(to)002:346: de nas ji ltar dar ba ni bye ma las /
NK129(to)002:347: gzugs ma dag pa la bshad /
NK129(to)002:348: gnyis kyis rgya gar gyi rgyal po in+t+ra b+hu ti la bshad /
NK129(to)002:349: de nas rgya gar gyi yul na dar shing rgyas par spyod do //
NK129(to)002:351: bal po sh+aakya de ba la bshad /
NK129(to)002:352: de gnyis kyis o rgyan rgyal po d+harma ko sha la bshad /
NK129(to)002:353: de nas o rgyan gyi yul na dar shing rgyas par spyod do //
NK129(to)002:354: bal po shi la many+dzusa smad mtshongs pa shin+ti la bshad /
NK129(to)002:355: des bal po'i rgyal po gu na ta ma la bshad /
NK129(to)002:356: de nas bal po'i yul na dar shing rgyas par spyod do //
NK129(to)002:357: da ni bod yul du ji ltar byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK129(to)002:359: bod kyi rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis /
NK129(to)002:360: bod yul du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'dzugs par dgongs nas /
NK129(to)002:361: thugs dam gyi lha khang bsam yas bzhengs pa'i sa
NK129(to)002:362: 'dul ba slob dpon bo d+hi sat+wa spyan drangs nas
NK129(to)002:364: bod kyi lha 'dre rnams zings langs te /
NK129(to)002:365: nyin mo mis brtsigs pa nub mo lha 'dres bshig te ri rdo ri la bskyal /
NK129(to)002:366: klungs rdo klungs su bskyal nas brtsigs tu ma bster ba dang /
NK129(to)002:368: e ma slob dpon byin brlabs chung ngam /
NK129(to)002:374: bdag ting nge 'dzin rtsal zhugs chung ba ma yin te /
NK129(to)002:375: byams pa shas ches pas mi ma yin ma thul ba yin /
NK129(to)002:376: o rgyan slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas zhes bya ba
NK129(to)002:377: rdo rje phur pa'i dngos grub thob pa cig bzhugs
NK129(to)002:378: / de spyan drangs na bar chad zhi bar 'gyur ro gsung /
NK129(to)002:379: de spyan mi 'drangs bsams zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:381: rang re rnams tshe sngon ma'i spun yin pas las dang smon lam gyi dbang gi byon yongs gsung /
NK129(to)002:382: de ji ltar yin zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:384: spyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sems can gyi don mdzad tshul bsam gyi mi khyab pa yin /
NK129(to)002:385: khyad par du 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyis sems
NK129(to)002:386: can thams cad 'khor ba nas drangs te lan gsum
NK129(to)002:387: du sangs rgyas kyi sa la bzhag ste /
NK129(to)002:388: da sems can 'khor ba na med dam snyam gzigs pas /
NK129(to)002:389: sngar bas kyang sems can mang zhing nyon mongs pa rags su song 'dug pas /
NK129(to)002:390: slar snying rje skyes te gshums pas /
NK129(to)002:391: 'chi ma thig pa gnyis gtor nas 'di gnyis kyi
NK129(to)002:392: sgo nas kyang sems can gyi don chen po ma
NK129(to)002:393: 'ongs pa'i dus na 'byung bar 'gyur cig ces gsungs
NK129(to)002:394: pas / 'chi ma thig pa gnyis sum cu rtsa gsum du song ba las /
NK129(to)002:395: lha'i bu mo gang+ga ma dang /
NK129(to)002:396: gang ga ma chung ngu zhes pa gnyis su skyes /
NK129(to)002:397: de gnyis cher skyes nas skabs su lha'i khrims bsrung ba zhig gi tshe /
NK129(to)002:398: gang+ga chung ngus gang+ga ma'i ldum ra nas me tog rkus pas /
NK129(to)002:399: lha'i khrims nyams pas tshe 'phos te /
NK129(to)002:400: skye ba phyi ma la mi'i yul du bya rdzi mo bde mchog bya bar skyes /
NK129(to)002:401: bya 'tshos pa'i sla dang rgyag lhags bsags te /
NK129(to)002:402: mchod rten bya rung kha shor zhes bya ba bzhengs /
NK129(to)002:403: bum pa'i srog shing btsugs tsam la mo shi nas /
NK129(to)002:404: dam tshig gi lha mo pra mo ha zhes bya bar sangs rgyas so //
NK129(to)002:405: de la bu bzhi yod te /
NK129(to)002:410: bu de bzhis mchod rten gyi 'phro rdzogs par 'byongs te grub /
NK129(to)002:411: rab gnas byas tshar ba dang /
NK129(to)002:412: bu so so'i smon lam 'di ltar btab po //
NK129(to)002:414: bdag cag tshos dge ba 'di la bstan nas skye
NK129(to)002:415: ba phyi ma la sa bdag gi rgyal po chen
NK129(to)002:416: po gcig tu skye bar gyur cig /
NK129(to)002:418: de'i 'og mas bstan pa bsrung pa'i basngagasa 'chang mthu stobs can gcig tu skye bar gyur cig /
NK129(to)002:419: de'i 'og mas mkhan po byang chub sems dpa' gcig tu skye bar gyur cig de'i 'og mas /
NK129(to)002:420: phu bo gsum po'i bya ba grub pa la gcig tu skye bar gyur cig /
NK129(to)002:422: de dus che ba rgyal po nyid yin /
NK129(to)002:425: de'i 'og ma yar klungs kyi sba khri bzhir yin gsungs /
NK129(to)002:426: de nas rgyal pos sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms /
NK129(to)002:428: shud bu dpal gyi seng ge gsum chib dang bcas
NK129(to)002:429: nas gser phye mang po bskur nas slob dpon spyan
NK129(to)002:431: de dus slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas rgya
NK129(to)002:432: gar d+aa hu la'i gtsug lag khang na 'khor pan+di
NK129(to)002:433: ta stong lnga brgya la rgyud lung man ngag gsum
NK129(to)002:434: gyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor zhing bzhugs pa las
NK129(to)002:435: / mngon par mkhyen pas mkhyen te /
NK129(to)002:437: da zla ba gsum na bdag bod kyi rgyal pos bla mchod pa 'gro bar 'dug /
NK129(to)002:438: chos rnams myur du tshar bar bya'o gsungs nas /
NK129(to)002:439: chos rdzogs pa dang zla ba gsum song ba nyin der /
NK129(to)002:440: bod kyi bang chen mi gsum po slebs /
NK129(to)002:441: gser gyi spa tra bco brgyad dang /
NK129(to)002:443: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i zhu ba rnams gsol bas /
NK129(to)002:444: sngon gyi smon lam gyis 'brel ba yod pas bod la 'dengs nas gnang ngo //
NK129(to)002:446: bod kyi mi gsum gyis d+aa hu la'i gtsug lag
NK129(to)002:447: khang nas bteg ste rim gyi bal yul du phebs
NK129(to)002:448: so // lang lab kyi lo rgyus su ni /
NK129(to)002:449: slob dpon spyan 'dren pa'i bang chen pa /
NK129(to)002:450: stag tshal gyi lo ts+aa ba brang ta dza ya rak+shi dang /
NK129(to)002:451: mang yul gyi lce ku ku ra tsa gnyis la gser phye bskur nas bardzangasa /
NK129(to)002:453: de nas rim gyi mang yul gyi grong khyer ze bya bar phebs /
NK129(to)002:454: de dus mang yul man khyim bdun las med /
NK129(to)002:455: rgan mo gsum la gdams pa btab pas skad cig la grol /
NK129(to)002:456: de dus bod kyi lha 'dre rnams kyi nyi ma phyed la nam bsros su bcug pas /
NK129(to)002:457: lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas skad cig la nyi ma dkug
NK129(to)002:458: nas zhag bdun nyi ma ma btang bar lha 'dre'i
NK129(to)002:459: kha non du khrong ze'i gong kha der lha khang
NK129(to)002:460: brtsigs / de la de dus mun pa lha khang zer ro //
NK129(to)002:461: de rtsa na chu mig gnyan po sus kyang reg
NK129(to)002:462: mi nus pa gcig yod pa de'i klu gtul nas
NK129(to)002:464: lha khang du thugs rje chen po bzhugs su gsol /
NK129(to)002:465: ri gong gcig tu bal po'i lha 'dre phyir 'brengs
NK129(to)002:466: pa rnams kyi kha gnon du rdo'i mchod rten bzhengs
NK129(to)002:467: phur pa gsum rdo la nub par btab nas bzhag
NK129(to)002:468: / de nas ya tshad na khung bu nas rlung
NK129(to)002:469: 'ong pa'i sa de bod la gnod par gzigs nas
NK129(to)002:470: lha khang brtsigs te mang yul byang srin yin no
NK129(to)002:471: / // de nas yar byon te ma chung gi bar du gsol /
NK129(to)002:472: der slob dpon la lha 'dres ma tshugs so //
NK129(to)002:473: khor rnams smyos pas smyon thang du grags so //
NK129(to)002:474: de 'dul ba'i don du mchod rten brgya rtsa brgyad mdzad do //
NK129(to)002:475: yang zhang zhung yul de gu ge la byon //
NK129(to)002:476: de gzhi bdag dgra lha mu tsa med kyis ma bzed nas /
NK129(to)002:477: ri phan tshun 'thab pa'i bar du slob dpon dpon g.yog bcar bar brtsams pas /
NK129(to)002:478: dpon g.yog rnams nam mkha' la gshegs /
NK129(to)002:479: dgra lha mu tsa med skrag ste bros pa las /
NK129(to)002:480: phyag mtshan rdo rje gsor bas /
NK129(to)002:481: mo drung du lhag ste srog snying phul bran du khas blangs te dam la btags so //
NK129(to)002:482: de nas lha yul gung thang du byon /
NK129(to)002:483: dge bsnyen nyi shu rtsa gcig gis cho 'phrul bstan /
NK129(to)002:485: thog me tog gi char du song nas /
NK129(to)002:486: der dge bsnyen rnams dbang du bsdus nas chos kyi bsrungs mar bskos so //
NK129(to)002:487: de nas mang yul kha la'i rong sgo ru /
NK129(to)002:488: bstan ma bcu gnyis kyis thog me da'u bcu gnyis dus cig la phab pas /
NK129(to)002:489: sdig 'dzub kyi rtse la blangs te klad la bskor bas /
NK129(to)002:490: sol dum bcu gnyis su nag hrul gyis song pas
NK129(to)002:491: bstan ma skrag ste srog snying phul dam la btags
NK129(to)002:492: / de dus gtso mo gangs dkar ma she'u gza'
NK129(to)002:493: bros te dpal mo lha mtsho'i nang du bros pas
NK129(to)002:494: / / slob dpon gyis dpal mtsho nas chu spar bu gang blangs nas /
NK129(to)002:495: dgongs pa gtad pas skad cig la spar bu'i chu
NK129(to)002:496: la rlangs pa chil gyis byung pa dang mtsho yang
NK129(to)002:498: spar bu'i chu de khol ba dang mtsho khol bas mos ma bzod te /
NK129(to)002:499: mtsho las brnyengs thon pa dang sha so sor bral nas keng rus su song ba dang /
NK129(to)002:500: phyag mtshan rdo rje 'phangs pas mig ya gcig bcar
NK129(to)002:501: de nas mo skrag nas srog snying phul sgrubs thabs
NK129(to)002:502: brtsams te / dkar mo gcig sgrub /
NK129(to)002:503: stag mo nu 'jag gnam sman mched lnga'i sgrub skor gsum du phye /
NK129(to)002:504: sngar bstan ma'i gtso mo yin pa la phyis rang mnyam du bzhag /
NK129(to)002:505: de nas rtsangs lhas lha phug tu bsnyen bskur nas bka' 'bangs su byas te /
NK129(to)002:506: 'di ni chos la tshud pas slob dpon la mtho ma mtshams so //
NK129(to)002:507: phug der stag gsum byung ba la rdo rje bsor
NK129(to)002:508: bas stag gsum po phug gcig tu bros song pa
NK129(to)002:509: la / shul brnyegs te byon pas rlung tshub gcig tu song pa la phur pa btab pas /
NK129(to)002:510: gas btsan gyis rang tshugs bstan nas srog snying phul lo //
NK129(to)002:511: phug pa de la stag phug ces da ltar yang grags so //
NK129(to)002:512: de rnams su lha 'dre thams cad bltar la brgyus
NK129(to)002:513: pa ltar dam la btags pas chu'i ming yang ltar
NK129(to)002:514: chu zhes grags / de nas lha 'dre'i khrom tshogs pas yul gyi ming la khrom pa zer /
NK129(to)002:515: de nas rtsums pa sbugs nas mar byon /
NK129(to)002:516: phug bdag mo gcig dge bsnyen du btsud /
NK129(to)002:517: de nas byang lam tshu tha nas byon /
NK129(to)002:518: stag gso lding gi kha nas grom pa lha khang gi rab gnas mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:519: grom pa rgyangs du de nas grags zer /
NK129(to)002:520: de nas rim gyis byang phyi khol na mar la byon /
NK129(to)002:521: 'od yug gro mo 'phrod kyi la kha ru lha srin gyi cho 'phrul byung pa btul /
NK129(to)002:522: de nas 'dam snying grong ngos la byon /
NK129(to)002:523: gnam mtsho dang thang lha'i bar du spra dkar phug nas bzhugs pas /
NK129(to)002:524: thang lhas thog char pa ltar phab /
NK129(to)002:525: slob dpon gyi sbra dkar rdo rje'i khang por bsgoms pas /
NK129(to)002:526: thog dred te mtsho la song bas /
NK129(to)002:527: mtsho khol te chu nang gi srog chags rnams shi /
NK129(to)002:528: der ngan song sbyong ba'i cho ga mdzad de sems can shi ba rnams byang chub la bkod /
NK129(to)002:529: de nas sbra dkar btab ste /
NK129(to)002:530: thang lha'i gang la zhal gzigs nas /
NK129(to)002:531: gangs kyi mgor ram gcig bsgoms pas gangs zhu nas
NK129(to)002:532: rud chad te g.ya' brag tu zang ste song ba
NK129(to)002:533: dang / kho skrag ste rang gzugs bstan nas srog snying phul /
NK129(to)002:537: bdag ni lha 'dre kun gyi sde dpon yin zer /
NK129(to)002:538: 'o na khyod kyi lha 'dre thams cad khrid shog
NK129(to)002:539: gsungs pas der khos lha 'dre phal che ba dkug
NK129(to)002:540: byung pa la / srog snying phrogs /
NK129(to)002:542: de nas gnam gyi shug sdong du dregs pa gnad 'bebs kyi sgrub pa zhag gsum mdzad /
NK129(to)002:543: nam srod la ri rab nyil pa lta bu'i sgra drag po byung ba dang /
NK129(to)002:544: thang lha dmag dpon bzhi 'khor dang bcas pas lhags so //
NK129(to)002:546: khyed la de tsam gyi sgra skad dang cho 'phrul yod na bzang gi /
NK129(to)002:547: khyod kyi khrod na pho bdud nyi khri chig stong dang /
NK129(to)002:548: de'i khrod na mthu che rtsal drag nyi shu rtsa gcig yod kyi /
NK129(to)002:549: de dag khrid la da lta nga'i drung du shog /
NK129(to)002:550: mi 'ong na khyed thams cad kyi srog snying nga la yod pas /
NK129(to)002:551: ngas thams cad kyi snying 'byin no gsungs pas thams cad skrag ste 'dar 'phril phril 'dug /
NK129(to)002:552: de nas dar cig na bdud la dbang che ba bzhi /
NK129(to)002:553: dmag dpon rnams rol dang lnga /
NK129(to)002:554: shar nas dbang che ba bzhi /
NK129(to)002:556: gnyan la dbang che ba bzhi /
NK129(to)002:557: klu rje thod dkar dang lnga /
NK129(to)002:558: btsan la dbang che ba bzhi /
NK129(to)002:559: yam shud dmar po dang lnga /
NK129(to)002:560: de dag gi las mkhan t+aak+ki nag po dang /
NK129(to)002:561: nyer gcig po dbang du bsdus /
NK129(to)002:562: dam nyams sgrol ba'i ging du bkos /
NK129(to)002:563: lha'i dge bsnyen du ming btags phur pa sgrubs pa'i
NK129(to)002:564: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi dgongs pa sgrub pa dang
NK129(to)002:565: dpal 'byor dang tshe spel bar khas blangs dam bcas
NK129(to)002:566: so // de nas phan yul gong gi la kha nas /
NK129(to)002:567: stod lung la log byon te /
NK129(to)002:568: stod lung gzhongs par chos ston gsol ba la chu med nas /
NK129(to)002:569: kha t+w+aam ga bye ma la rgyab pas chu rko mog bdun byung /
NK129(to)002:570: da lta gzhong pa lha chu bya bar grags /
NK129(to)002:571: gzhan yang stod lungs kyi yul rnams su btsan dang /
NK129(to)002:573: the'u rang rnams dam la btags /
NK129(to)002:574: de nas lha sa gram thang du byon nas zhag gcig bzhugs /
NK129(to)002:575: der phyibs la rtsa med pa la /
NK129(to)002:576: lha sa'i bye ma skad cig la ne'u sing du bsgyur nas phyibs kyi rtsa byung ste /
NK129(to)002:577: ding sang kyang ne'u sing du yod pa 'di yin /
NK129(to)002:578: de nas skye chu brgal te ba lam klags kyi la la byon pa dang /
NK129(to)002:579: phyi blon rnams kyi mnga' bdag la /
NK129(to)002:580: slob dpon byon no zhes sbran /
NK129(to)002:582: nga bod kyi btsan po yin yang /
NK129(to)002:583: slob dpon o rgyan gyi rgyal po'i sras yin /
NK129(to)002:584: sangs rgyas rnams dang mi lab pa bzhin du gsungs glengs mdzad pa /
NK129(to)002:585: lha ma srin bran du mkhol ba sogs yon tan
NK129(to)002:586: mtha' yas pa yin pas bsu ba la 'gro dgos
NK129(to)002:587: dgongs nas / dbu la zhwa dang /
NK129(to)002:589: na bza' steng g.yogs ber ske rags ma bcings par g.yangs klubs su gsol nas byon tsa na /
NK129(to)002:590: slob dpon yi zhal nas la nye mi bzang /
NK129(to)002:591: dus nam zhig na stod na rgyal khrims zhwa tsam ga cig chags pa 'dug /
NK129(to)002:592: smad na rgyal khrim lhwam tsam gcig lus par 'dug /
NK129(to)002:593: bar 'dir rang kha sil bu sil bur 'gro bar 'dug /
NK129(to)002:594: kye hud sems can snying re rje /
NK129(to)002:596: dus der phan tshun phyag brnyeg res byung pas /
NK129(to)002:597: slob dpon gyi rgyal po la dbu dun mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:598: rgyal po'i na baza'i phyed mes bzhob tu rog par song /
NK129(to)002:599: phyag mkhar dum bu gsum du chag /
NK129(to)002:600: der rgyal po'i thugs la rdzu 'phrul dang yon tan slob dpon lhag mod /
NK129(to)002:601: nga bod ru bzhi'i rje yin pas phyag la lan 'ong ngam dgongs pa la /
NK129(to)002:602: slob dpon gyi srid lag gi sen mo la gling
NK129(to)002:603: bzhi gling phran thams cad khongs su bcug nas bstan
NK129(to)002:604: / nga che nga btsan gyi mgur gsungs pas /
NK129(to)002:606: de nas bsam yas kyi sa 'dul mdzad te brtsigs /
NK129(to)002:608: mtshan mo lha 'dres brtsigs pas legs par 'byongs te rab gnas mnga' gsol mdzad /
NK129(to)002:609: rgyal po rje 'bangs rnams kyi dga' ston lo bcu gsum du byas so //
NK129(to)002:612: jo mo mkhar chen bza' dang /
NK129(to)002:613: spyan 'dren pa mi gsum gyis rdo rje phur pa'i dbang nos /
NK129(to)002:614: rgyud dang sgrub thabs mnyan te /
NK129(to)002:615: phur pa rgyal po lugs su grags pa dang /
NK129(to)002:619: jo mo lugs bzhi ru byung /
NK129(to)002:620: des rjes rong ban la gnang bas /
NK129(to)002:621: rong zong lugs dang mkhon la gnang ba las mkhon
NK129(to)002:622: gyi lugs deng sang sa phur du grags pa 'di
NK129(to)002:624: cog ro zas slob dpon dngos la thug kyang dbang
NK129(to)002:625: yi dam la zhus pas yi dam slob dpon gyi
NK129(to)002:626: thugs khar 'dus pas dbang bskal chad /
NK129(to)002:627: phyis jo mo mtsho rgyal gyis thugs brtse bas /
NK129(to)002:628: man ngag zab dgu gnang bas phur pa lcam lugs zhes 'byung ba de yin no //
NK129(to)002:629: de'i nang nas 'byung pa'i drag sngags gza' gdong dmar nag zhes grags pa /
NK129(to)002:630: snubs pa dang rje btsun mi la'i mthu chen po
NK129(to)002:631: de yang phur pa lcam lugs kyi gdams skor yin
NK129(to)002:632: te ding sang gi bar du lung rgyun yod do
NK129(to)002:633: // de nas brag dmar bsam yas su slob dpon
NK129(to)002:634: gyis phyi nang chos rgya chen po gsungs pa'i dus
NK129(to)002:635: // / jo mo mkhar chen bza' lha mo la bsrung ma'i sprul pa yin par gzigs /
NK129(to)002:636: rgyal pos kyang gzung mar phul /
NK129(to)002:637: der slob dpon gyi jo mo la /
NK129(to)002:638: khyod la 'og min gyi zhing khams bstan gyi gsungs nas /
NK129(to)002:639: slob dpon dang gnyis 'ja' ltar du yal nas song /
NK129(to)002:640: zhag gsum song pa'i nang par log nas byung /
NK129(to)002:642: khyed kyi 'og min gyi zhing khams mthong ngam gsungs pas /
NK129(to)002:643: bdag gi kun tu bzang po'i zhing khams dang /
NK129(to)002:650: mi bzad pa rgyan gi 'khor lo bsam gyi mi khyab pa bstan te mthong zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:653: slob dpon gyi 'og min gyi zhing khams spyod mi nus /
NK129(to)002:654: de nus pa yin na gzugs kyi phung po la mi chags pa yin te /
NK129(to)002:655: slob dpon da dung gzugs kyi phung po la chags 'dug pa gsungs pas /
NK129(to)002:657: bdag gi mthong pa'i zhing khams de rnams kyi bkod pa 'di dang 'di lta bu bda'/
NK129(to)002:660: sngon bdag gi ma gyim shang kong jo ma bde spyod rgyal po la gtod pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)002:661: ge sar rgyal po'i lag tu bdag gi me'i 'phrul
NK129(to)002:662: gyi me long bse'i phub chung tsam zhig shor nas
NK129(to)002:663: yod kyi / de slob dpon len du chug cig gsungs /
NK129(to)002:664: jo mo'i slob dpon la de brjod ma thag tu slob dpon 'od du yal /
NK129(to)002:665: rjes shel phreng brgya rtsa brgyad bgrang ma zin pa
NK129(to)002:666: la slob dpon gyis ge sar rgyal po'i bang mdzod
NK129(to)002:668: de jo mos rje la phul /
NK129(to)002:670: rgya mtsho'i ting na klu'i rgyal po gtsug na /
NK129(to)002:671: rin chen gyi bu mo mdzes ldan ma'i lag na yid bzhin gyi nor bu yod kyi /
NK129(to)002:672: de slob dpon len du chug gsung /
NK129(to)002:673: jo mos de skad brjod ma thag /
NK129(to)002:677: bar snang khams na sbrang khams pa'i rnga ma yod kyi /
NK129(to)002:678: de slob dpon len chug gsung /
NK129(to)002:679: sngar ltar skad cig la blangs /
NK129(to)002:681: zhang po rgya'i yul na sngon bskal pa bzang po'i nang tshad dang /
NK129(to)002:682: tshe lo bcu pa'i bre tshad yod kyi gsungs /
NK129(to)002:683: de yang skad cig la blangs byung yang rje'i zhal nas /
NK129(to)002:684: rdo rje gdan na sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK129(to)002:685: dri ma med pa'i sku'i gdan khri'i bar gyis sa
NK129(to)002:686: 'og na gnam chags pa'i dum bu bya ba dang
NK129(to)002:687: / sa ral pa'i ras ma bya ba'i dum bu
NK129(to)002:688: rin po che yod kyi de slob dpon len chugs
NK129(to)002:689: / gsung / jo mos slob dpon la brjod ma thag tu blangs byung pa rje la phul bas /
NK129(to)002:691: slob dpon gyi rdzu 'phrul gyi khungs brtags pa yin te /
NK129(to)002:693: slob dpon 'di 'byung ba dang rang sems la dbang thob pa /
NK129(to)002:694: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas las lhag pa cig 'dug gsung /
NK129(to)002:695: thugs rje zhabs spyi bor blangs so //
NK129(to)002:696: de'i dus su rgyal po rje 'bangs rnams kyi tshe
NK129(to)002:697: snga ma'i skye ba ji ltar blangs pa'i tshul dang
NK129(to)002:698: / de'i rgyu mtshan blon po khri bzang yab lhag khyod /
NK129(to)002:699: skye ba 'di yi snga ma la /
NK129(to)002:700: nya yi lus ni blangs pa'i rtags /
NK129(to)002:701: da lta mchan khung g.yon na nya gshog yod /
NK129(to)002:702: zhes sogs gsung pas kun yid ches /
NK129(to)002:703: da lta rang rang so so bsam pa 'di ltar 'gyur tshul dang /
NK129(to)002:704: ma 'ongs dus kyi 'gyur ldog la sogs pa dus
NK129(to)002:705: gsum sa ler gzigs pas chags thogs med par lung
NK129(to)002:706: bstan / dus 'dir lo ts+aa ba brang ti dza ya rak+shi ta dang /
NK129(to)002:707: lce ku ku r+aa tsas byas nas chos mang du bsgyur /
NK129(to)002:708: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug la phur pa gnang bas /
NK129(to)002:709: des rgyud kyi don khongs su chud /
NK129(to)002:710: gdan 'dren pa mi gsum gyis kyang brgyud kyi bshad pa rgya cher spel te /
NK129(to)002:711: sna snam gyi gtsang du spel /
NK129(to)002:712: shud bus lho brag tu bshad /
NK129(to)002:713: mchims kyi kongs yul mchims kyi steng du spel lo //
NK129(to)002:714: de tsam gyis bsam yas 'chings bur slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dang /
NK129(to)002:715: de'i lo ts+aa ba snyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ras byas te /
NK129(to)002:716: rje 'bangs nyer lngas sgrub chen byas pa la /
NK129(to)002:717: dar za byang chub kyis sgrub pa la ya ga bsgrags nas chab gsol dgos zer /
NK129(to)002:718: de blon po rnams kyi btsad po la zhus /
NK129(to)002:719: khyad par ngan lam stag ra klu gong gis slob
NK129(to)002:720: dpon la ngan smras mang du byas pas kho kha
NK129(to)002:721: lkugs / dar za byang chub ni sa'i lha mo bstan ma phag ser khra la zhon /
NK129(to)002:722: lag na lcags kyu thog pas dar za'i lce nas
NK129(to)002:723: btab ste gson por sa 'og tu khrid pa kun
NK129(to)002:724: gyis mthong bas blon po rnams kyis slob dpon la
NK129(to)002:726: bstan pa ma nub tsam du byung /
NK129(to)002:727: der slob dpon rdzu 'phrul dang mthu stobs che bas /
NK129(to)002:728: bod kyi blon po chos la mi dga' ba rnams yid rab tu bskrag ste /
NK129(to)002:729: slob dpon slar rgya gar du byon pa'i zhu ba rgyal po la phul /
NK129(to)002:730: sdig blon rnams dbang ches pas rgyal po yang gsan dgos pa byung nas zhal gyis bzhes /
NK129(to)002:732: nga rgya gar du 'gro ba rung mod kyi /
NK129(to)002:733: 'on kyang gsang sngags rnying ma'i bstan pa yongs rdzogs spel ma thub pas glo ba ma dga'/
NK129(to)002:734: bod kyi ri thams cad nags kyi khyab pa /
NK129(to)002:736: bye ma thams cad ne'u gsing du bsgyur ba /
NK129(to)002:738: byang thang thams cad zhing la btang ba sogs bya rgyu mang po yod pa la /
NK129(to)002:739: sems can gyi bsod nams la ma shong ba yin /
NK129(to)002:741: bsam yas kyi mtha' bskor bya ma la bsnyen phur bsgril bas sing mar sngo zhungs kyi song /
NK129(to)002:742: gtsug lag khang dang lcags ri mtha' la bskor ba mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:743: zhabs bzhag pa'i sar lcang ma re skyes so //
NK129(to)002:745: bstan pa bsrung ba'i drag sngags brgya rtsa brgyad dang /
NK129(to)002:746: phan bya brgya nyi shu gnang /
NK129(to)002:747: 'dzam bu'i gling gi nor kun bsdus nas rgyal po
NK129(to)002:748: dpe dkar la gtad de bsam yas kyi bsrung mar
NK129(to)002:749: bskos / de nas slob dpon gshegs khar /
NK129(to)002:751: bdag bud med blo dman pas nyung la bslab chos gcig zhu /
NK129(to)002:752: nyon mongs pa rags pas nyon mongs 'joms pa'i chos gcig zhu /
NK129(to)002:753: tshe thung bas grub thag nye ba'i chos gcig zhu /
NK129(to)002:754: dgra mang bas mthu che ba'i chos gcig zhu /
NK129(to)002:755: zhes zhu don bzhi phul bas /
NK129(to)002:756: nyung la bsdus pa phur pa rtsa ba'i dum bu stod las byang chub sgrub pa /
NK129(to)002:757: smad las smod pa lam du khyer ba man ngag mchog tu gyur pa 'di gnang ngo //
NK129(to)002:760: da ni bdag srin po'i kha gnon la 'gro ba'i dus la bab pa 'dra'o //
NK129(to)002:761: bdag ni tshe'i rig 'dzin thob pa yin /
NK129(to)002:762: mnga' bdag nyid kyang tshe'i dngos grub 'dod na tshe
NK129(to)002:763: chu 'di 'thung mdzod gsungs nas bdud rtsi bum pa
NK129(to)002:764: gang gnang / der rgyal po'i dgongs pa la /
NK129(to)002:765: slob dpon gshegs par chas pa 'dis ma dges na /
NK129(to)002:766: lho bal gyi zhas kyis dug btang ba 'dra'ang srid snyam /
NK129(to)002:767: spyang thul gyi 'dabs nas mar phebs pas de ma thag pa la chu mig brdol bas /
NK129(to)002:768: ding sang chu rjes ne'u sing du grags so //
NK129(to)002:769: de nas slob dpon gshegs pa mnga' bdag gi ma bzod te /
NK129(to)002:771: rgyal po bdag nyid ma gum bar du bzhugs par zhu /
NK129(to)002:773: bsam yas su rgyun du bzhugs par ma gnang /
NK129(to)002:774: ma 'ong pa'i 'gro ba skal ldan rnams kyi don
NK129(to)002:775: du bod sgrub gnas rnams su rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i
NK129(to)002:777: sgrub pa mdzad te byin gyis barlobasa pa dang /
NK129(to)002:778: bod khams gling dgu'i sa gzhi thams cad zhabs kyis
NK129(to)002:779: btags te bkra shis shing byin chags par bya ba
NK129(to)002:780: dang / da dung bod kyi gdul bya ma rdzogs pas /
NK129(to)002:781: de dag gi don gyi phyir dben gnas gang dang ri brag mtsho gling rnams su gnas bcas te /
NK129(to)002:782: rgyal po rje 'bangs kyi don du skabs skabs su 'ong gis /
NK129(to)002:783: nga'i chos kyi 'phro lus pa rnams rgya gar nas
NK129(to)002:784: slob dpon bi ma la mi tra spyan drangs nas
NK129(to)002:786: jo mo mtsho rgyal gyi nye gnas byas te gshegs so //
NK129(to)002:787: de nas sgrub gnas rnams su byon nas sgrub pa mdzad /
NK129(to)002:788: brag la sku dang zhabs kyi rjes bzhag /
NK129(to)002:789: khyad par du mtsho chen po bzhi la phyag rjes
NK129(to)002:790: bzhag pa ni chu ma skams kyi bar du gnas
NK129(to)002:792: bsam yas kyi rab gnas dang /
NK129(to)002:793: skabs su rgyal po rje 'bangs la chos gsung ba dang /
NK129(to)002:794: btsun mo dmar rgyan baza'i mdze nad gsal ba rnams la byon /
NK129(to)002:796: sras mu ne btsan po yum gyis dug gis bskrongs /
NK129(to)002:797: mu khri btsan po na bzhon matha'i dmag rgya dang /
NK129(to)002:800: khrom la sogs pas bod phung la nye ba na /
NK129(to)002:801: rgyal khrims lo gsum brkyangs te bod 'bangs kyi don mdzad /
NK129(to)002:802: mthar rgyal bu la rgyal sa gtad de /
NK129(to)002:803: de nas su yis bshol btab kyang ma gsan te /
NK129(to)002:804: lho nub rnga yab kyi gling du srin po'i kha mnon la gshegs te /
NK129(to)002:805: de lta bod yul 'dir ji tsam bzhugs snyam na /
NK129(to)002:806: sba bzhed du bshad pa ltar bsam yas kyi sa
NK129(to)002:807: 'dul ba la sogs pa'i bar du zla ba gsum
NK129(to)002:808: bzhugs / de nas rgya gar la gshegs pa ltar
NK129(to)002:809: du sdig blon rnams kyi ngor mdzad nas bod dben
NK129(to)002:811: zla ba drug gi bsgred pa re la lo dang zhag bco lnga la zla ba rer rtsi ba /
NK129(to)002:812: rgyal po lo chos la sogs pa rgya gar gyi
NK129(to)002:813: rtsis lugs gcig gis dbang du byas pa'i lo brgyad
NK129(to)002:814: dang bcu gcig / lo hriil po lnga bcu rtsa lnga dang zla ba drug bzhugs pa yin no //
NK129(to)002:815: don 'di nyid thugs su ma chud cing /
NK129(to)002:816: lo rgyus la go ba ma longs pa dag gis /
NK129(to)002:817: myang gi gter dpe bee ro'i phyag bris ma las /
NK129(to)002:818: slob dpon pad+ma bod yul du lo brgya dang bcu gcig bzhugs te /
NK129(to)002:819: zhes pas rgyal po'i bla mchod du lo brgya dang /
NK129(to)002:820: sgrub gnas rnams su lo bcu gcig bzhugs so //
NK129(to)002:822: rgyal po'i dgung lo drug cu rtsa brgyad bzhugs par khas len mod kyi /
NK129(to)002:823: de ltar na lugs de'i lo bcu dgu po de
NK129(to)002:824: la gong gi mdzad pa de rnams rdzogs pa yul
NK129(to)002:825: med la / mdzad pa de dag ji ltar mdzad
NK129(to)002:826: pa'i tshul ni ding sang gi bar du phal che
NK129(to)002:827: ba rnams mngon sum du gsal bas shes so //
NK129(to)002:828: spyir slob dpon 'di'i yon tan dang 'phrin las dang
NK129(to)002:829: gdul bya 'dul tshul ni 'phags pa sa bcu pa
NK129(to)002:830: la gnas pa rnams kyis kyang bsam par mi nus
NK129(to)002:831: shing sangs rgyas rnams kyi bskal pa brgya'i bar du
NK129(to)002:832: gsung kyang rdzogs mtha' mngon pa yin par rgya bod
NK129(to)002:834: slob dpon de la phur pa'i slob ma mang yang /
NK129(to)002:835: mchog tu bka' babs pa ni jo mo mtsho rgyal yin te /
NK129(to)002:836: des mon kha ne ring seng ge rdzong gi brag
NK129(to)002:837: phug tu phur pa'i dkyil 'khor zhal phye ste sgrub
NK129(to)002:838: pas zhag nyer gcig na phur pa thams cad bzhad
NK129(to)002:839: cing 'od 'phro ba dang bro phrab pa byung /
NK129(to)002:840: der jo mo'i dgongs pa la /
NK129(to)002:841: ma mo grub na khrag zor 'phang //
NK129(to)002:842: gshin rje grub na 'khor lo bskor //
NK129(to)002:843: ging pho grub na las la rbad //
NK129(to)002:844: phur pa grub na btab las bya /
NK129(to)002:846: bdag la brdo ba'i dgra ni med /
NK129(to)002:847: su la brdeg gam snyam ste bsnyen phur bsgril ba las /
NK129(to)002:848: bdag la dgra med kyang pha mes kyi srog gcod
NK129(to)002:849: pa'i za 'dre la bdab snyam du dgongs pa dang
NK129(to)002:850: / bsnyen phur phyag nas shor te nam mkha' la phur nas /
NK129(to)002:851: pha yul gyi khang pa'i ltag na 'dre de gnas pa'i skyer phung cig yod pa la babs te /
NK129(to)002:852: skyer phung de rtsa ba nas bsregs cing za 'dre de nyid bsgral /
NK129(to)002:853: phur pa de dbon brgyud rnams kyis bcangs te /
NK129(to)002:854: gdengs pa rtsam gyis lha 'dre mang po btul bas /
NK129(to)002:855: mkhar chen gza' 'dre 'dul gyi rgyud pa zhes zam ma chad pa byung ngo //
NK129(to)002:856: jo mo 'di ni sgrol ba tshad du phyin pas /
NK129(to)002:857: mtshon gyis bsad pa'i mi ro yang gson por bslangs nus pa yin no //
NK129(to)002:858: de nas ji ltar brgyud pa ni /
NK129(to)002:859: jo mos rang gi ming po mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug la bshad /
NK129(to)002:860: des la byid ye shes brtsegs /
NK129(to)002:861: des lce ston yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK129(to)002:865: des rma chu rab kyi pha rol /
NK129(to)002:866: skye chu rab kyi tshur ro //
NK129(to)002:867: dbye ma yug mo sgang du lang lab byang chub
NK129(to)002:868: rdo rje la bshad te de yan chig brgyud kho
NK129(to)002:869: na yin la / phur pa man ngag drug pa zhes bya ba'i rgyud pa yin /
NK129(to)002:870: de nas lang lab kyis bka' bo ba sna snam shes rab tshul khrims /
NK129(to)002:871: bka' rkus pa myang nag dbang gi shes rab zhes grags kyang /
NK129(to)002:872: de'i dus kyi slob dpon so so'i chags sdang gi gtam yin gyi /
NK129(to)002:873: myang nag la bka' bo ba'i lo rgyus 'og tu 'chad do //
NK129(to)002:874: de nas sna snam gyis rgya ston sangs rgyas la bshad /
NK129(to)002:875: des bshangs gur zhogs khams pa lung du rgya thung shes rab rgyal mtshan la bshad /
NK129(to)002:876: de'i nag po rmu'i brag phug tu dgon ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan la bshad te /
NK129(to)002:877: 'dis ni sna snam shud bu 'chims gsum gyi gdung rgyud la yang thug nas zhus so //
NK129(to)002:878: phur pa la 'di bas mkhas pa ma byung zhes grags //
NK129(to)002:879: des myang dar ma seng ge la bshad /
NK129(to)002:880: des snubs shes rab ye shes la /
NK129(to)002:881: des rang gi sras snubs bdud rtsi 'od la /
NK129(to)002:882: des sras phur grags la bshad /
NK129(to)002:883: des sras jo lcam la bshad /
NK129(to)002:897: bla chen chos kyi rgyal po /
NK129(to)002:898: de la bdag gi man ngag drug pa'i dbang dang gdams skor rnams kyi lung mnos /
NK129(to)002:899: yang lang lab kyi slob ma kyi ban byang chub rin chen bya ba gcig byung /
NK129(to)002:900: de la pha spun rnams kyi khang zhing dang nor phrog pa la bsten nas /
NK129(to)002:901: lang lab la phur pa zhus sgrub nas /
NK129(to)002:902: pha spun gyi mi grong tsho dgu'i mi phyugs sgo khyi tshun chad tshar bcad de /
NK129(to)002:903: mthar dgra 'di tsho shi bas mi chog /
NK129(to)002:904: khang pa'i gyang 'di mthong pa dang yang nga snying na gsungs nas /
NK129(to)002:906: gyang kun kyang rmangs nas 'gyel te /
NK129(to)002:907: de nas mtshan yang kyi gyang 'gyel du grags /
NK129(to)002:908: de'i slob ma khams pa stong gsum gyi bsgom chen mu ne dang /
NK129(to)002:909: thag gdong dkar gyi btsun pa shes rab 'od gnyis
NK129(to)002:910: las mched de shin tu mthu che ba kyi phur
NK129(to)002:912: ding sang ni gdams bskor thor bu las /
NK129(to)002:913: yongs su rdzogs pa bzhugs pa'i bka' lung yod pa ma rnyed do //
NK129(to)002:915: thag btsun sher 'od kyi slob ma lha rje snubs chung yin par bshad par ltar na /
NK129(to)002:916: gza' gdong dmar nag gi skor yang kyis lugs la yod dam snyam mo /
NK129(to)002:928: 'o bran la sogs pa'i rus chen rnams kyi gdung rigs las /
NK129(to)002:929: rdo rje phur pa'i sgrub pa thob pa ni bod
NK129(to)002:930: yul 'dir shin tu mang zhing brjod kyis mi lang
NK129(to)002:931: la gsar ma'i sngags rnams ma dar gyi bar du
NK129(to)002:932: yid dam dang bstan bsrung gi srog rtsa yang phur
NK129(to)002:934: brgyud pa byin gyis rlobs pa'i sngags 'chang de rnams
NK129(to)002:935: gdung rigs shas che ba las gsar ma ba'i skyes
NK129(to)002:936: chen rnams kyang byon pa yin te /
NK129(to)002:937: bstan pa'i bdag po sa skya pa dang /
NK129(to)002:939: phag mo grub pa la sogs pa lta bu ste /
NK129(to)002:940: de ltar byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK129(to)002:941: so so'i gdung rabs rnam thar rnams su gzigs par mdzod kyi //
NK129(to)002:942: bdag cag shes rab chung ba dag gis brjod par mi nus so //
NK129(to)002:943: da ni rang lugs la grags pa rong zom lugs kyi lo rgyus cung zad brjod par bya ste /
NK129(to)002:944: de la phur pa'i chos 'di rong zom la ji ltar brgyud pa ni /
NK129(to)002:947: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug /
NK129(to)002:948: don +aa tsar+ya dpal gyi me tog /
NK129(to)002:951: rong ban yon tan rin chen /
NK129(to)002:952: rong ban rin chen tshul khrims kyi bar du brgyud pa las 'ong ba yin la /
NK129(to)002:954: rong ban yon tan rin chen gyis /
NK129(to)002:955: slob dpon pad ma dngos la thugs /
NK129(to)002:956: des mi yul du lo gsum brgya bzhugs te mthar sku ma spangs par mkha' spyod du gshegs /
NK129(to)002:957: de'i sras rong ban rin chen tshul khrims kyis kyang lo phyed dang nyis brgya bzhugs /
NK129(to)002:958: de'i sras rong zom yin la /
NK129(to)002:959: 'dis lo brgya dang bcu dgu mi yul du bzhugs
NK129(to)002:960: sku bgres rgud mi mnga' ba'i ngang nas sku gshegs
NK129(to)002:961: pa yin zer / gang ltar yang grub thob bar ma chad pa'i brgyud pa yin la /
NK129(to)002:963: bod ru bzhi'i nang nas ru lag gtsang smad kyi sa'i cha /
NK129(to)002:965: sku gzhon nu nas sgra tshad la sogs pa shes bya thams cad la mkhas shing /
NK129(to)002:966: gzhan bdag dngos po stobs kyi rigs par tshar bcad pas /
NK129(to)002:967: kha gcig pan+di ta smri ti'i skye ba yin zer /
NK129(to)002:968: kha gcig pan+di ta 'phra la ring mo'i skye ba yin zer /
NK129(to)002:969: phyis jo bo rje dang rong yul lhar mjal te
NK129(to)002:970: brtsod pa byas pas jo bos rong zom ma thub
NK129(to)002:972: khyed rgya gar gyi +aa tsar+ya nag po zhabs chen spyod pa bde'i skye ba yin te /
NK129(to)002:973: kho bos khyod dang chos kyi gtam bya bas ga la thub ces gsungs /
NK129(to)002:974: ngo mtshar ba'i mdzad pa dang cho 'phrul la thogs pa med pas /
NK129(to)002:975: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa'i sprul par yang grags la /
NK129(to)002:976: phal cher 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa yin zhes basngagasa brjod do //
NK129(to)002:977: 'dis dgung lo bcu gcig mtshan nyid gsan /
NK129(to)002:978: bcu gsum yan chad la gsan pa rdzogs te mkhas pa'i phul du phyin /
NK129(to)002:979: ma slabs pa'i shes bya thams cad yang ma rmongs /
NK129(to)002:980: dka' ba'i gnas rnams kyang lan re nyan pas mkhyen pa yin te /
NK129(to)002:982: bdag thos pa chung ba yang ma yin te /
NK129(to)002:983: chos thams cad la ma thos pa med do //
NK129(to)002:984: bdag thos pa che ba yang ma yin /
NK129(to)002:985: chos tha mas cad la tshar re las ma dgos so //
NK129(to)002:987: spyir na dam pa 'di shes rab zab la rgya che ba dri ma med pa dang ldan pas /
NK129(to)002:988: rgya gar gyi chos su rtogs pa mdo rgyud bstan
NK129(to)002:989: bcos sngar ma gzigs pa dag la yang tshar re
NK129(to)002:990: re gnyis gzigs pas mkhyen nas /
NK129(to)002:991: tshig don ma lus pa thugs su chud cing mi brjed pa'i gzungs thob pa yin no //
NK129(to)002:992: gzhan yang tsa na ka la sogs pa 'jig rten lugs kyi bstan bcos dang /
NK129(to)002:996: rig byed kyi bstan bcos gzhan gsum dang /
NK129(to)002:997: sa rtags pa la sogs pa'i shes bya phra mo mtha' dag la yang mkhas shing /
NK129(to)002:998: thugs rje chen po mnga' bas chos la mos pa'i mi rnams dang /
NK129(to)002:1000: rdo rje theg pa la zhugs pa dag gis las
NK129(to)002:1001: dang dngos grub sgrub par 'dod pa rnams la phyin
NK129(to)002:1002: ci ma log pa'i gdams pas nan tan du phan
NK129(to)002:1003: thog pa mdzad / mngon par shes pa'i cha dang
NK129(to)002:1004: ldan zhing sems can 'dul ba'i dus dang tshod la
NK129(to)002:1005: thog pa mdzad / mkhas / 'gro ba phal pa
NK129(to)002:1006: dang chos kyis blo bsgyur ba rnams tshe 'di dang
NK129(to)002:1007: phyi ma gnyis ga bde ba la 'god pa'i phyir
NK129(to)002:1008: bstan bcos mang du brtsam shing /
NK129(to)002:1009: de ltar bus phan 'dogs pa la dus rtag tu skyo ba mi mnga'/
NK129(to)002:1010: chos kyi blo ma bsgyur ba'i skye bo phal pa
NK129(to)002:1011: la yang ser sna dang gnod sems spangs nas thugs
NK129(to)002:1012: rje'i yul du mdzad de zhi bde la 'god //
NK129(to)002:1013: sdom pa dang thugs dam la srog ltar gces spras su mdzad cing /
NK129(to)002:1014: gzhan bdag kyang de la sbyor /
NK129(to)002:1015: chos rtsom pa na gleg bam bsdu zhing gzigs pa la sogs pa'i brtsol ba ma mdzad kyang /
NK129(to)002:1016: chos phyogs med la thogs sdug med pa'i spobs pa spro bar nus /
NK129(to)002:1017: bstan bcos mdzad pa de dag kyang lung dang rig
NK129(to)002:1018: pa dang mi 'gal zhing sgra skyon dang don skyon
NK129(to)002:1019: dang rnam par bral bas gzhan mkhas pa sus kyang
NK129(to)002:1020: brtsod mi nus / sgra'i tshul dang sang+k+ri ta'i skad ma bslabs par mkhyen /
NK129(to)002:1021: byis pa'i dus su a tsa ra byung tshad la dgyes shing de dag gi skad la mkhas /
NK129(to)002:1022: bi brti' po ti gzigs pas skad dod kyi bag chags sad pa ltar gyur /
NK129(to)002:1023: tha na dud 'gro'i skad dang brda' yang mkhyen /
NK129(to)002:1024: 'khrul pa mi mnga' zhing byin rlabs che bas des
NK129(to)002:1025: mdzad pa'i gsang sngags kyi yig cha rnams la slob
NK129(to)002:1026: ma'i brgyud du byung ba'i gang zag rnams kyis lung
NK129(to)002:1027: ma thob par yi ge las byung ba bzhin du
NK129(to)002:1028: sgrubs pa la byin brlabs dang dngos grub ma byung
NK129(to)002:1029: ba med / lo ts+aa ba chen po de la
NK129(to)002:1030: dus de'i tshe bod ru bzhi'i mkhas pa mang pos
NK129(to)002:1032: go rub lo ts+aa ba dge slong chos kyi shes
NK129(to)002:1033: rab ces bya ba chos phyogs med la mkhas pa
NK129(to)002:1034: zhig gis / thog mar bod du skyes pa'i gang
NK129(to)002:1035: zag gi chos mang po brtsoms pa zhes bskur pa
NK129(to)002:1036: zhig gis / btab bo // phyis bla ma rong
NK129(to)002:1037: zom gyis mdzad pa'i theg pa chen po'i tshul la
NK129(to)002:1039: gus pa chen po skyes te /
NK129(to)002:1040: zang zing mang pos mnyes pa byas te nyes pa bshags nas bdag rjes su bzung du gsol /
NK129(to)002:1042: 'jam dpal gsang rgyud la sogs pa chos mang du zhus pas gnang /
NK129(to)002:1043: gzhan yang mar pa chos kyi dbang phyug la sogs pa'i lo ts+aa ba dang /
NK129(to)002:1044: mkhas par grags pa'i blo rtsal can mang pos btud cing gsan par gyur te /
NK129(to)002:1045: gsan pa po de bdag gi slob rgyud thams cad
NK129(to)002:1046: kyang shin tu dad nas bla dam par 'dzin no
NK129(to)002:1047: // gsang rgyud kyi skabs su nyid kyi zhal nas /
NK129(to)002:1048: 'o skol da ltar rgya dpe yod na 'di ltar 'gro ba yin te /
NK129(to)002:1049: rgya dpe med pas da lta bcos su med gsungs pa la /
NK129(to)002:1050: go rub kyi dpe bzungs nas /
NK129(to)002:1051: phyis jo bo krish+na pa zhes bya ba'i pin+da ta las rgya dpe byung nas de las gsan pas /
NK129(to)002:1052: rong pa chen po gsung pa bzhin byung nas shin tu mos te /
NK129(to)002:1053: krish+na pa las byung pa'i dpe gcig rong pa nyid la phul nas yang gsan skad /
NK129(to)002:1055: pin+da ta many+dzu sh+r+ai war+m+ma dang /
NK129(to)002:1057: u p+aa ya sh+r+ai mi tra dang /
NK129(to)002:1058: bud d+ha +aa ka ra b+ha dra dang /
NK129(to)002:1059: de n+aa ka ri tsan+t+ra dang /
NK129(to)002:1060: pa ra me sho ra dang /
NK129(to)002:1061: a mo g+ha badz+ra la sogs pa pan+di ta mang pos bstan nas /
NK129(to)002:1062: de dag gi lo ts+aa ba mdzad te /
NK129(to)002:1066: bde mchog rtsa rgyud la sogs pa mang du bsgyur /
NK129(to)002:1067: 'gyur shin tu bzang bas phan che bar btags /
NK129(to)002:1068: pan+di ta kun gyi gsung nas kyang /
NK129(to)002:1069: d+har+m+aa b+ha tra khyod kyis chos mang po brtsoms la 'gro ba rnams skyobs shig /
NK129(to)002:1070: khyod kyi yon tan gzhan lta zhog gi /
NK129(to)002:1071: sgra tshad kyi lugs 'di'i sum cha tsam las mi
NK129(to)002:1072: shes pas kyang rgya gar na chos mang po brtsoms
NK129(to)002:1073: pa yin khyod ci'i phyir chos mi brtsom zhes gsungs
NK129(to)002:1074: / de lta bu'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan yang /
NK129(to)002:1075: bdag bstod la sogs pa'i dri ma dang bral zhing /
NK129(to)002:1076: gzhan gyi chos lugs dang spyod pa dman yang don
NK129(to)002:1077: du 'gyur na ma gtogs pha rol khyad du gsod
NK129(to)002:1079: brag bzang po'i ngo la gshegs pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1081: brag la phur pa 'debs pa la sogs pa'i rdzu 'phrul dang grub rtags la thogs pa mi mnga'/
NK129(to)002:1082: myang smad du 'gar ston tshul khrims bzang po la sngags rnying ma gsan te /
NK129(to)002:1083: 'di dgung lo bcu gnyis pa'i dus yin /
NK129(to)002:1084: lo bcu gsum pa la mkhas pa mdo ston seng ge rgyal mtshan la yang gsan /
NK129(to)002:1085: rnal lam du gsang ba snying pos zan byas /
NK129(to)002:1086: sangs rgyas mnyams sbyor gyi tshod ma byas gsol ba smis pa slob dpon la zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:1087: de shin tu bzang chos de khongs su chud pa'i rtags yin /
NK129(to)002:1088: de gnyis la khyod kyis 'grel pa re gyis gsungs pas /
NK129(to)002:1090: bod du yig cha byung ba la bzang /
NK129(to)002:1091: dus phyis bstan bcos mdzad pa ni /
NK129(to)002:1092: bslab pa rin po che gsum la bsten pa'i ched du gal che ba'i man ngag gsum mdzad te /
NK129(to)002:1093: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi slab pa rgyud la skye ba'i phyir dam tshig mdo rgyas mdzad /
NK129(to)002:1094: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis bslab pa bskyed pa'i
NK129(to)002:1095: phyir 'brel ba tshul bzhi yan lag bco lnga pa
NK129(to)002:1096: mdzad / lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa rgyud
NK129(to)002:1097: la bskyed pa'i phyir rdzogs pa chen po blta bsgom
NK129(to)002:1098: mdzad / man ngag mdzad / gzhan yang ngan song spyod rgyud dang /
NK129(to)002:1100: smra sgo la sogs pa yang 'grel ba mdzad cing /
NK129(to)002:1101: bstan bcos gzhan yang mang du mdzad /
NK129(to)002:1102: de'i dus su shab kyi yang khye bla ma /
NK129(to)002:1110: rgya rgyal tshul la sogs pa bod ru bzhi'i mkhas pa rnams kyis brtsod par brtsams te /
NK129(to)002:1111: bod ru skyes pa'i gang zag gi bstan bcos 'di
NK129(to)002:1112: tsam brtsams pa mi rigs so zhes zer zhing bsun
NK129(to)002:1114: gsungs gling mdzad pa tsam gyis rtsod pa'i spobs pa bcom /
NK129(to)002:1115: bstan bcos re mthong bar shin tu mos te /
NK129(to)002:1117: zhabs tog mdzad de bstan gyi skyabs gnas su mdzad par gyur to //
NK129(to)002:1118: de ltar rong zom 'di ni 'khrungs pa tsam nyid
NK129(to)002:1119: nas ngang gis dge ba'i kun spyod can lhun gyis
NK129(to)002:1121: 'jig rten lugs kyi thugs dkyil yang shin tu che
NK129(to)002:1122: zhing rang dang dus mtshungs kyi mkhas pa thams cad
NK129(to)002:1124: phyi nang gi rig pa'i gnas mtha' dag la mkhas /
NK129(to)002:1125: khyad par sgra tshad la ma rmongs pas /
NK129(to)002:1127: 'di ni don 'di tsam zhig la 'jug go zhes
NK129(to)002:1128: tshig don gyi khyad par phra mo dag kyang gzhan
NK129(to)002:1129: las ches lhag par ston nus /
NK129(to)002:1130: mdo rgyud bstan bcos bod du 'gyur ro cog gi
NK129(to)002:1131: tshig don ma lus pa thugs su chud cing mkhas
NK129(to)002:1132: / tha na 'jig rten pa'i mtsho tshis zhing las /
NK129(to)002:1134: dkar she sgrub pa sogs la'ang mkhas pas /
NK129(to)002:1135: de dag ji ltar bsgrub pa'i bstan bcos kyang mdzad /
NK129(to)002:1136: bod kyi lha 'dre thams cad kyis kyang chos zhu zhing bsnyen bskur bka' bsgrub /
NK129(to)002:1139: bstan pa'i bdag por gyur pa yin te /
NK129(to)002:1140: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi chos thams cad kyang mnga'/
NK129(to)002:1141: bee ro ts+aa na'i chos rnams kyang /
NK129(to)002:1142: bee ros g.yu sgra snying po /
NK129(to)002:1143: des bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal /
NK129(to)002:1144: des gru ma shing slag can nas /
NK129(to)002:1147: des rong zom la bshad des /
NK129(to)002:1148: sems kyis brgyud pa lugs gcig kyang mnga' ste bstan pa'i bdag por gyur /
NK129(to)002:1149: ldan klongs thang sgron mar sku 'khrungs pa'i sprul pa'i
NK129(to)002:1150: sku a ro ye shes 'byung gnas kyis gdams pa'i
NK129(to)002:1152: 'di la rgya gar bdun brgyud dang /
NK129(to)002:1153: rgya'i hwa zhang bdun brgyud kyi gdams pa yod pa las /
NK129(to)002:1154: a ro'i dngos slob cog ro zangs dkar mdzod khur
NK129(to)002:1155: dang khams pa ya zi bon ston gnyis ka la
NK129(to)002:1157: de nas rgyud pa tsho la rdzogs chen khams lugs su grags /
NK129(to)002:1158: bi ma la las brgyud pa rnams kyang /
NK129(to)002:1161: snyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra nas brgyud pa dag kyang /
NK129(to)002:1162: snyags dang rma gnyis kas khu byang chub 'od dang /
NK129(to)002:1163: khyung po dbyig 'od las rim par 'ongs te rong zom la mnga'/
NK129(to)002:1164: mdor na 'di'i mkhyen pa dang yon tan ni sus kyang brjod du mi nus shing /
NK129(to)002:1165: bod gangs can gyi rgyud 'dir 'di dang mnyam pa'i mkhas pa ni su yang ma byung la /
NK129(to)002:1166: spyir 'di sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa yin mod kyi /
NK129(to)002:1167: grub pa thob pa ni rdo rje phur pa'i sgo nas yin pas /
NK129(to)002:1168: phur pa'i bstan bcos kyang mang du mdzad de /
NK129(to)002:1169: brgyud pa rnams kyang grub thob zam ma chad par byon pa yin la /
NK129(to)002:1173: dang por rong ban dpal gyi rin po che /
NK129(to)002:1174: de'i sras rong ban rin chen tshul khrims /
NK129(to)002:1175: de'i sras rong zom chos kyi bzang po dang /
NK129(to)002:1177: chos bzang gi sras gzi brjid 'bar ba dang 'bum 'bar gnyis /
NK129(to)002:1178: gzi brjid 'bar gyi sras ston dar dang ston skyabs gnyis /
NK129(to)002:1179: ston dar la sras ston song /
NK129(to)002:1180: ston seng gi sras jo sras ra spe /
NK129(to)002:1182: ston skyabs kyi sras jo sras 'od zer /
NK129(to)002:1184: chos bzang gis sras gnyis pa 'bum 'bar la sras chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK129(to)002:1186: jo bzang sogs kha yar byung /
NK129(to)002:1187: chos kyi rgyal mtshan gyi sras su +aa nan+da badz+ra ste /
NK129(to)002:1190: des yi sras chos kyi gshes gnyen dang /
NK129(to)002:1192: rong pa jo bzang gi sras slob dpon jo bkra /
NK129(to)002:1195: dar bzang gi sras slob dpon ser 'od /
NK129(to)002:1196: jo brtan gyi sras nyi ma seng ge /
NK129(to)002:1197: des sras 'od zer 'bum dang 'bum rgod gnyis /
NK129(to)002:1198: rong bsgom chos 'phags kyi sras slob dpon ston g.yung /
NK129(to)002:1199: de'i sras jo sras lha bsrungs /
NK129(to)002:1200: de'i slob dpon byams chos pa chen po dar ma brten /
NK129(to)002:1201: de'i sras slob dpon sra brtan rdo rje yin no //
NK129(to)002:1202: deng sang ni rong zom gyi gdung brgyud chad nas med kyang /
NK129(to)002:1203: 'bum rgod kyi dus su rin spung ba'i zhal ngo nam mkha' rgyal po'i sbyin bdag mdzad te /
NK129(to)002:1205: de'i nang nas mchog tu gyur pa thang khrom bka' bzhi pa yin te /
NK129(to)002:1207: rong zom chos bzang gi gdung 'bum dgon dkar por spyan drangs /
NK129(to)002:1208: phur pa'i chos bskor snyags kyi gdung brgyud sngags 'chang sle ma ba rnams la gsungs so //
NK129(to)002:1210: spyir dam pa 'di de dus kyi mkhas grub thams
NK129(to)002:1211: cad kyi zhabs la btug pas bsam gyi mi khyab
NK129(to)002:1212: cing / khyad par du go rub lo ts+aa ba /
NK129(to)002:1214: rje 'gos la sogs pa lo ts+aa ba chen po bcu bdun /
NK129(to)002:1215: g.yag rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs pa grub thob
NK129(to)002:1216: chen po gsum cu rtsa lnga ma gcig zha ma'i
NK129(to)002:1217: ming po rje mkhon phu ba la sogs pa bsgom
NK129(to)002:1218: chen grub pa thob pa brgya brgyad cu /
NK129(to)002:1219: yol dge bsnyen rdo rje dbang phyug dang /
NK129(to)002:1220: yang khyer bla ma la sogs pa ston pa gdugs
NK129(to)002:1221: thogs pa lnga brgya la sogs pa mtha' yas te
NK129(to)002:1222: brjod kyis mi lang ba lta bu las phur pa'i
NK129(to)002:1223: chos bskor ji ltar brgyud pa ni /
NK129(to)002:1224: rong zom gyis yol dge bsnyen rdo rje dbang phyug /
NK129(to)002:1237: lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho /
NK129(to)002:1239: bla ma dam pa rdo rje seng ge /
NK129(to)002:1240: de la bdag gi rong zom lugs kyi dbang lung rdzogs pa zhus so //
NK129(to)002:1241: da ya phur pa lha nag tu grags pa ni /
NK129(to)002:1242: slob dpon pad+ma yab yum yan chad spyid dang 'dra la de nas /
NK129(to)002:1244: 'di ni phur pa'i sgo nas grub pa thob ste
NK129(to)002:1245: tshe'i rig 'dzin brnyes pas ding sang gi bar du
NK129(to)002:1246: 'das grongs med par bzhugs pa yin la /
NK129(to)002:1247: lang lab byang chub rdo rjes grub pa thob tshar ba'i rjes su'ang 'di dang mjal nas /
NK129(to)002:1248: sngar thos pa'i phur pa'i skor la zhus dag byas /
NK129(to)002:1249: tshar gcig zhus dag yin cing /
NK129(to)002:1251: ngam 'bre a tsa ra sa le yin par byas 'dug pa ni ma nges pa chen po ste /
NK129(to)002:1252: mtsho rgyal dang lang lab kyi bar na mi rabs lnga yod pa ma go ba yin la /
NK129(to)002:1253: gter ma'i lo rgyus gcig na /
NK129(to)002:1254: lang lab lo bdun 'gro ba'i byis pa gcig gis /
NK129(to)002:1255: slob dpon lho nub tu byon khar zhabs la btugs zer ba snang ste /
NK129(to)002:1256: ma nges pa'i rang bzo kho na'o //
NK129(to)002:1257: phyis 'gro ba'i mgon po chos rgyal 'phags pas /
NK129(to)002:1258: smad las drag po sgrol ba'i dbang 'di gsan par bzhed nas brtsal bas ma rnyed de /
NK129(to)002:1259: 'khor rnams la 'di lta bu'i dbang thob pa 'dug na sprang po zhig la 'dug kyang khrid shog /
NK129(to)002:1260: de la kho bos zhu'o gsungs nas brtsal kyang ma rnyed /
NK129(to)002:1261: phyis bal po nas tshong pa'i skad cha las /
NK129(to)002:1262: jo mo mtsho rgyal gyi slob ma a lo rgyus gzhan las /
NK129(to)002:1263: bal po'i pan+di ta rat+na sh+r+ai yin zer /
NK129(to)002:1264: tsa ra nu ru bya ba tshe rig 'dzin thob pa zhig la phur pa'i chos rdzogs par bzhugs /
NK129(to)002:1265: bal po na gsung gi 'dug zer /
NK129(to)002:1266: der bstan pa'i khur chen po dgongs pas /
NK129(to)002:1267: 'o na de bal por yod dam gsungs pas med /
NK129(to)002:1268: bsil ba tshal la sogs pa'i gnas rnams su mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi don mdzad pa yin zer /
NK129(to)002:1270: gdul bya bskal pa can rnams la chos bag re gsung pa brda' zer ba la /
NK129(to)002:1271: 'o na de bal por byon na nga la skad
NK129(to)002:1272: theng pa gyis gsung ste gnang sbyin mang po snang
NK129(to)002:1273: / de nas lo 'ga' song ba dang /
NK129(to)002:1275: der 'phags pa rin po che chos dang 'jig rten
NK129(to)002:1276: gyi thugs brel gyis g.yengs nas 'byon ma thub nas
NK129(to)002:1277: / glo bo lo ts+aa ba shes rab rin chen
NK129(to)002:1278: la gser la sogs pa'i dngos po mang po bkur
NK129(to)002:1279: / nas bardzangasa / de nas lo ts+aa ba bod
NK129(to)002:1280: du byon pa dang 'phags pa rin chen drag po'i
NK129(to)002:1282: ding sang gi bar du ma nub pa 'di yang /
NK129(to)002:1284: 'phags pa rin po che drin yin no //
NK129(to)002:1286: ya 'brog pa gu rub yang dag gis rgyud mya
NK129(to)002:1287: ngan las 'das pa zhes bya ba 'di la brten
NK129(to)002:1288: nas lha thams cad nag por mdzad pa las byung
NK129(to)002:1290: de'i gong gi brgyud pa ni /
NK129(to)002:1293: sna snam tshul khrims shes rab /
NK129(to)002:1297: gu rub yang dag /'gos ston byang 'bar /
NK129(to)002:1301: skyi chos kyi se nga ge /
NK129(to)002:1302: rgya ye shes kyi mgon po /
NK129(to)002:1303: dpal ldan rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK129(to)002:1304: 'dis bshad 'bum rdo rje don gsal dang /
NK129(to)002:1306: sgrub skor la sogs pa yig sna mang du mdzad /
NK129(to)002:1307: des bla ma tshul rgyal ba /
NK129(to)002:1308: ri gdongs pa shes rab rgyal mtshan /
NK129(to)002:1309: slob dpon bsod nams bzang po /
NK129(to)002:1310: slob dpon bkra shis rgya mtsho /
NK129(to)002:1312: sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i mtshan can bla ma chen po rdo rje rgyal po /
NK129(to)002:1313: bla ma rdo rje seng ge /
NK129(to)002:1314: de la bdag gi zhus so //
NK129(to)002:1315: yang gu rub nas brgyud nas phur pa lha nag ni /
NK129(to)002:1317: snye mdo pa la babs te 'phrin las che bar byung ngo //
NK129(to)002:1318: deng song gi bar du bstan pa'i bdag po dpal
NK129(to)002:1319: ldan sa skya pa rnams phyag len du mdzad pa'i
NK129(to)002:1320: sa phur du grags pa ni /
NK129(to)002:1321: dang por mkhon klu dbang bsrung pas slob dpon pad+ma
NK129(to)002:1322: dngos la zhus nas sgrubs pas grub pa thob ste
NK129(to)002:1323: / 'di'i gcung mkhon rdo rje rin chen ni phur
NK129(to)002:1324: pa la brten nas grub pa thob cing de'i sras
NK129(to)002:1332: mkhon rog shes rab tshul khrims /
NK129(to)002:1333: 'di ni lha srin bran du 'khol zhing /
NK129(to)002:1334: yi dam mang po zhal gzigs /
NK129(to)002:1335: rnga la zhon te nam mkha' la 'gro ba la
NK129(to)002:1336: sogs pa rdzu 'phrul thogs med du ston nus pa
NK129(to)002:1337: yin la 'di yan chad du phur pa'i grub pa
NK129(to)002:1338: thob pa sha stag byon no //
NK129(to)002:1339: mkhon rog 'di'i gcung po mkhon dkon mchog rgyal po yin te /
NK129(to)002:1340: 'dis 'gro'i lung ston chen po zhig la ltad mo la byon pas /
NK129(to)002:1342: dbang phyug nyer brgyad kyi mchams byas pas khro thog chod /
NK129(to)002:1343: de'i lo rgyus gcen la bsnyad pas /
NK129(to)002:1344: da gsang sngags 'chol ba bya ba'i dus byung pas grub thob mi 'ong /
NK129(to)002:1345: rang re la yod pa'i dpe cha lha rten sngags kyi lag cha kun gter du sba /
NK129(to)002:1347: khyod ni gzhon pa yin pas /
NK129(to)002:1348: mang kar du 'brog mi lo ts+aa ba la gsang
NK129(to)002:1349: sngags gsar ma nyon shog gsungs nas rnying ma kun
NK129(to)002:1350: gter du sbas / der chos skyong gi cho 'phrul ches pas /
NK129(to)002:1351: phur pa'i mngon rtog skor bsdus pa gcig /
NK129(to)002:1352: yang dag gi dpe mtshan gcig /
NK129(to)002:1354: seng ldeng phur pa skor cha gnyis /
NK129(to)002:1355: dkar mo nyi zlas mkhon rog la dngos su bstan
NK129(to)002:1356: pa'i sgrub skor rnams 'don dgos pa byung ste bcung
NK129(to)002:1357: la gnang / 'di'i sras sa skya pa chen po yin la /
NK129(to)002:1358: de nas rje btsun su mched /
NK129(to)002:1360: 'phags pa rin po che nas rim par brgyud nas ding sang gi bar du dar rgyas che la /
NK129(to)002:1361: bla chen chos kyi rgyal po'i drung du bdag gis
NK129(to)002:1362: kyang ldong ston gyii yig cha'i steng nas sa phur
NK129(to)002:1363: gyi dbang dang / chos skor sna 'ga' re thos so //
NK129(to)002:1364: yang gsang ba'i rgyud phur pa la bsten pa mtha' dag nas btus pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1366: k+ai l+ai ya'i tan+t+ra bcu gnyis nas btus pa bshams sngon gyi skor du grags pa /
NK129(to)002:1367: stod las yang dag la brten nas byang chub bsgrub pa 'i tshul dang /
NK129(to)002:1368: smad las sras mchog phur pa la bsten nas dgra
NK129(to)002:1369: bgegs bsgrol ba'i rim pa dang por bal yul yang
NK129(to)002:1370: le shod du slob dpon rnam pa gsum du mdzad
NK129(to)002:1371: / bod yul du slob dpon pad+ma bsnams byon pa dus der spel ba'i dus la ma bab nas /
NK129(to)002:1372: byang gi bya mang po'i sa'i cha la gter tu sbas /
NK129(to)002:1373: dus phyis gter gton byang chub gling pa dpal rgyal
NK129(to)002:1374: mtshan gyis gter nas thon te ding sang lung rgyun
NK129(to)002:1375: yod la / pan chen bi ma mi tra nas brgyud te dar ba'i tshul ni /
NK129(to)002:1376: bod chos skyong ba'i rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan sku gshegs rjes /
NK129(to)002:1377: btsun mo dmar rgyan gza' me tog sgron dbang che zhing spyod pa ngan pas /
NK129(to)002:1378: sngags kyi lo ts+aa ba kun la sdang zhing btses pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1381: snyags la sogs ba bsam yas su ma bzhugs par /
NK129(to)002:1383: yul gyi matha'i dben pa rnams na bzhugs la /
NK129(to)002:1384: khyad par du snyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra ya 'brog sgang du bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)002:1385: rang gi pha spun so snyams dge la ston gyi
NK129(to)002:1386: 'dis mu stegs ngan sngags mkhan sdig po che yin
NK129(to)002:1387: no zhes yul mi kun la sgrog /
NK129(to)002:1388: ban da zung gcig bse zhos byugs nas dmar por yod pa de gnyis brkus nas /
NK129(to)002:1389: ban da gri rtses 'drud cing mi rnams la ston /
NK129(to)002:1390: 'dis zog 'dis 'dra byed do zer ya ga bsgrags /
NK129(to)002:1392: dben pa shig pa'i gros bshams pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1393: slob dpon gyis do dgongs nas /
NK129(to)002:1394: gang du dgongs pa mdzad pa'i sar rin po che gtor zhing bzhag pas /
NK129(to)002:1396: slob dpon gang na dgongs pa mdzad pa'i shul kyang rin po che 'phrul lo //
NK129(to)002:1397: khyod kyi de mi bden no zer ba la /
NK129(to)002:1399: mi bden na 'di re zer zhing yang ben de gri rtses 'grud cing bston no //
NK129(to)002:1400: der slob dpon yul der ma chags nas g.yog po
NK129(to)002:1401: glal mi da 'og brtsan bya ba zhig khrid nas
NK129(to)002:1402: // kong po mchi ma yul gyi steng du byon pas /
NK129(to)002:1412: lung ston gi ra la bdag po ga la mchis /
NK129(to)002:1414: ra mchims bya rog gi yin pas /
NK129(to)002:1418: ra la bdun 'jal sbrad tsa na /
NK129(to)002:1419: ma nyan par dben pa bshig /
NK129(to)002:1420: lcags kyi tho ba thogs nas dad pas slob dpon bros te /
NK129(to)002:1422: btsun chung gi mgo la lcags tho de'i de thebs zer ro //
NK129(to)002:1423: der yang bzhugs su ma chags nas /
NK129(to)002:1424: bod yul dbus su byon pas /
NK129(to)002:1425: slob dpon rta gcig chibs nas mas nas byon pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1426: 'gro sras chung sha ba gcig ded nas yas nas byung pa dang thug phrad pas /
NK129(to)002:1430: nyams ban 'dis nga'i sha ba yang shor /
NK129(to)002:1432: rta brdabs kyang brtsal zer nas ded te gsod par chas pa la /
NK129(to)002:1434: dus de rtsa na mnga' bdag gi sras che ba mu ne btsan po la /
NK129(to)002:1435: yum dmar brgyan bzas dug btang ste bskrongs /
NK129(to)002:1436: de'i lhad kyi tshogs dpon la slob dpon bi ma la rgya nag nas spyan drangs 'dug /
NK129(to)002:1437: der bi ma'i spyan sngar phyin nas /
NK129(to)002:1438: gser phye long mo gang phul /
NK129(to)002:1440: lo ts+aa ba dpon g.yog skyid dam gsungs pa la /
NK129(to)002:1441: ya 'brog sgang du skyi bgyi ru //
NK129(to)002:1442: dge la ston gyi mar bster ro //
NK129(to)002:1443: mchims yul sting du skyid bgyi ru //
NK129(to)002:1444: bya rog smyal bas ma bster ro /
NK129(to)002:1445: bod yul dbus su skyid bgyi ru /
NK129(to)002:1446: 'bro sras chung gi ma bster ro //
NK129(to)002:1447: zhes bsnyags kyis glu phul bas /
NK129(to)002:1448: bi ma las bstan pa nub kyi dogs nas /
NK129(to)002:1449: phur pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1450: bshams sngon ma bu gnyis thugs nas phyungs te gnang /
NK129(to)002:1451: lho brag g.yar chu sna'i brag phug tu seng ldeng
NK129(to)002:1452: phur pa nyi shu rtsa gcig la bsten te bi
NK129(to)002:1453: ma la dang / snyags lo ts+aa ba gnyis gas
NK129(to)002:1454: sgrubs pas phur bu khrol ba la sogs pa'i mtshan
NK129(to)002:1456: der snyags kyis thog mar bya rog la'o byas nas phur pa bsgril bas /
NK129(to)002:1457: stong khams kyi bya rog thams cad 'ub 'ub 'dus byung /
NK129(to)002:1459: mchims bya rog la'o byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1460: mchim yul steng gi bya rog zung gcig byung der
NK129(to)002:1461: snyags khros nas bya rog gcig la btabs par brtsams
NK129(to)002:1462: pa dang / bya rog tshub ling gis shi'o /
NK129(to)002:1464: da slong la thong byas pas bslong ma thub /
NK129(to)002:1465: der bi ma las bye ma gcig btab nas bslongs te btang /
NK129(to)002:1466: da phyin chad de tsug ma byed sdig che'o gsungs nas /
NK129(to)002:1467: gnas lung gi cho ga yang der gnang ngo //
NK129(to)002:1468: de nas 'chims lha than tsho g.yag dkar po gcig
NK129(to)002:1469: tu byas nas byung ba la yang phur pa btab
NK129(to)002:1470: nas bsgral / mchims bya rog kyang der bsgral /
NK129(to)002:1471: bsla bcang rab la btab pas rab bskam /
NK129(to)002:1473: tha ma la btab pas tha ma bskams /
NK129(to)002:1477: snag gi gnyen mtshams yan chad la btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1479: dam sri'am sku dgra rnam pa gcig der brtul lo //
NK129(to)002:1480: dam sri rnams pa gcig ni /
NK129(to)002:1481: pha spun so snyags dge la ston la btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1482: slob dpon snyags nyid snying rje skyes klongs su gyur pas ye ma thebs te /
NK129(to)002:1483: phur pa'i mtshan dang ldan pa zhig snyed na thebs 'ong gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1484: der tshol du phyin pas dus de tsa na 'khar ba la sog po zer bas /
NK129(to)002:1485: sog po chen po zhig gis sha zhig dang shing khur gcig khur /
NK129(to)002:1486: ra gcig khrid pa dang phrad /
NK129(to)002:1488: bdag gi rus ni khang lags /
NK129(to)002:1489: ming ni stag sbyin lags zer /
NK129(to)002:1492: de khab nag brdung gnyis mid pas /
NK129(to)002:1494: khyod kyi chos nus sam gsungs pas /
NK129(to)002:1495: bka' brtsal na barngo thogs lags zer ro /
NK129(to)002:1496: nang par ben+d+ha gzhan zhig 'gar tshang du byung ba
NK129(to)002:1497: la kam pas khab tsag rgyab pas a tsha zer
NK129(to)002:1498: / mdangs rgong gi ben+d+ha de ni khab mid nas kyang btong /
NK129(to)002:1499: khyod a tsha zer ba ci nyeg zer rgod do //
NK129(to)002:1500: bar der chung ma la barngana pa sbyin nas khyod la gros thob cig byas /
NK129(to)002:1501: de nas kho la chos bya'am bgyis pas /
NK129(to)002:1502: chung ma la dris 'o zer dris pas /
NK129(to)002:1504: chos mi bya ba'i gtsug ga na yod /
NK129(to)002:1505: chos ni dmar srang khri tsho res kyang mi khugs zer /
NK129(to)002:1506: der chos bskor bzhugs pa la yo byed med zer ba la /
NK129(to)002:1507: yo byed slob dpon gyis chungs nas chos sbyin pas /
NK129(to)002:1508: kho dad pa mchog tu skyes te rab tu byung /
NK129(to)002:1509: ming lha dpal gyi ye shes su btags /
NK129(to)002:1510: 'di phur bu'i mtshan dang ldan pa ni /
NK129(to)002:1516: ro smad zur gsum du yod pa /
NK129(to)002:1517: ci la yang thogs pa med pa zhig snyed /
NK129(to)002:1518: de dang mthun pa 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu la yang 'dug pas /
NK129(to)002:1519: sngar gyi slob ma yang yin pas gnyis ga khrid de 'ongs /
NK129(to)002:1520: de nas dpon slob gsum gyis bsgrub pa byas nas bsgral /
NK129(to)002:1521: slar yang sog po dpal yes snyags dge la ston gyi gam du song pas /
NK129(to)002:1522: kho shi 'dug pa'i snying gton nas slob dpon la phul te /
NK129(to)002:1523: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK129(to)002:1524: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK129(to)002:1525: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK129(to)002:1526: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK129(to)002:1527: kun kyang gnod pa rnams dang bral //
NK129(to)002:1528: zhes ched du brjod de gnas spar /
NK129(to)002:1529: snyags lha bya rmangs lcags kyi bya khra gcig tu byas byung ba yang bsgral /
NK129(to)002:1530: bla spyang rab 'bring tha ma gsum ga la btab ste bskams /
NK129(to)002:1531: bran dang 'og rta sgo khyi brnag gi gnyan mtshams tshud chad bsgral /
NK129(to)002:1532: dam sri rnam pa gcig der btul lo //
NK129(to)002:1533: de nas 'bro sras chung ne'u thang na rta khyu 'tsho ba las /
NK129(to)002:1534: rnam shes ling ga la dkug nas phur pa btab ste bsgral /
NK129(to)002:1535: 'bro'i lha spyang sku sngon po zhig tu byas byung ba yang bsgral /
NK129(to)002:1536: bla spyang rab 'bring tha ma gsum la btab pas bskams /
