NK129(to)002:1537: bran dang 'og rta sgo khyi rnag gi gnyen mtshams yan chad la btab nas bsgral te /
NK129(to)002:1538: dam sri rnam pa gcig der btul lo //
NK129(to)002:1539: tshul 'di la lo rgyus la lar /
NK129(to)002:1540: snyags dz+ny+aan ku m+aa ra la sku dgra gsum langs pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)002:1541: 'o phran dpal gyi gzhon nu'i dkor nor dang zhing yul la sogs pa phul /
NK129(to)002:1542: brtul zhugs dang dpa' rtsal gyis slob dpon gyi thugs bzung /
NK129(to)002:1543: yab mched po snyags dge la ston dang /
NK129(to)002:1544: snyags 'phags pa smyug zhu can gnyis kyis /
NK129(to)002:1545: gcen gshes bsnyen lha mtsho btson du bzungs nas /
NK129(to)002:1546: brtson bsrung mi gnyis bzhag pa la /
NK129(to)002:1547: 'o bran gyis brkus nas slob dpon la phul bas mnyes te phur pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1548: bsham sngon can gnyis ga nang pa yin zer ro //
NK129(to)002:1551: btson du bzung ba ni yul nya 'khor gyis mda' ngam ra zhes par /
NK129(to)002:1552: ngam ra dang pha spun mi sha chags pa la /
NK129(to)002:1553: chos rgyal bzhugs dus snyags la brtsod ma nus pa las /
NK129(to)002:1554: phyis btsun mos sras dang lo ts+aa ba rnams dbu 'phangs dmad dus /
NK129(to)002:1555: snyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra nyid btson du bzung ba /
NK129(to)002:1556: sog po dpal ye srog la ma bltas par btson bsrung mi gnyis bkum nas /
NK129(to)002:1557: slob dpon btson nas bton pa yin pas /
NK129(to)002:1558: gcen lha mtsho btson du bcug pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1559: 'don pa po 'o bran dpal gzhon yin zhes pa nor ba yin la /
NK129(to)002:1560: phur pa phun sum tshogs pa bshams sngon dang bcas pa'i chos skor kyang /
NK129(to)002:1561: 'o bran kho na la yod pa las gzhan la ma grags pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)002:1562: snyags la dpal gyi slob ma brgyad byung ba'i brgyad
NK129(to)002:1563: ka la yod par phur pa'i lo rgyus kyi yi
NK129(to)002:1564: ge rnying ma dag las gsal lo //
NK129(to)002:1565: dpal gyi slob ma brgyad ni /
NK129(to)002:1568: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug /
NK129(to)002:1569: thag bzang dpal gyis rdo rje /
NK129(to)002:1571: zla lcogs dpal gyi seng ge /
NK129(to)002:1572: dar rje dpal gyi grags pa /
NK129(to)002:1573: lha lung dpal gyi rdo rje rnams yin no //
NK129(to)002:1576: mnga' ris su mched pa grangs las 'das pa byung bar bshad /
NK129(to)002:1577: de tsho'i nang nas 'brog mi ral pa can gyis
NK129(to)002:1578: sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che rten dge slong
NK129(to)002:1579: la rgyud pas phrin las che bar grags shing /
NK129(to)002:1580: 'di dag ni slob rgyud shas che'o //
NK129(to)002:1581: gdung brgyud kyi dar rgyas byung pa la yang mang ngo //
NK129(to)002:1582: de dag tu ma 'dus pa'i mchog gi slob ma ni /
NK129(to)002:1583: 'o bran dang sog po dpal ye dang /
NK129(to)002:1584: snyags kyi dbon rgyud rnams yin te 'phrin las rgya che zhing rgyun mi chad pa byung zhing /
NK129(to)002:1585: khyad par grub thob zam ma chad par byon no //
NK129(to)002:1586: de dag la lung rgyun dbang dang 'brel pa ma chad tsam bdag gis rnyed pa ni /
NK129(to)002:1587: 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu sku 'das nas zla ba lnga drug nas /
NK129(to)002:1590: yab mes kyi phyag dpe rnams gzigs pas dad te /
NK129(to)002:1591: lung rgyun rtsad bcad pas ring mo zhig lon pa na /
NK129(to)002:1592: gye re gnyen rtse'i ri khrod na snubs ston pad+ma dbang rgyal la bzhugs zer /
NK129(to)002:1594: gser srang bco brgyad kyis sna drangs pa'i 'bul ba
NK129(to)002:1595: mang po byas nas lo gnyis la rdzogs par zhus
NK129(to)002:1596: / chig brgyud bka' rgya dang gser gyi 'bul ba med par mi ster bas /
NK129(to)002:1597: 'o bran gyi phur pa gser mgo can du grags shing /
NK129(to)002:1598: gzhan yang gshin rje gshed 'thob rgya can gyis skor dang /
NK129(to)002:1599: mdo rgyud sems gsum la sogs pa snubs pa la brgyud pa 'ded do //
NK129(to)002:1600: de nas bla mes dbang phyug gis rang gi yab 'o bran pad 'byung la yang gsan /
NK129(to)002:1601: chos 'phro cung zad ma rdzogs pa la yab gshegs pas snubs kyi slob mar /
NK129(to)002:1603: snyags pad+ma rgyal po la rdzogs par gsan te brgyud pa gnyis ldan du byed de /
NK129(to)002:1604: de nas sprul sku ri rab dam pa'i bar du 'o bran gyis gdung brgyud rnams la brgyud cing /
NK129(to)002:1605: ri rab dam pas rin po che don grub dpal 'byor la gnang /
NK129(to)002:1606: de nas rim par brgyud de /
NK129(to)002:1607: yongs 'dzin dam pa rdo rje seng ges bdag la
NK129(to)002:1608: phur pa phun sum tshogs pa shams sngon dang bcas
NK129(to)002:1609: pa thugs brtse bas gnang ngo //
NK129(to)002:1610: da ni phur pa gzhan la ma grags pa jo
NK129(to)002:1611: bo lang lab kyi khyad chos ji ltar byung ba
NK129(to)002:1612: ni / lang lab kyi bla ma ngam 'bre sa le yan chad ni gong du bstan zin la /
NK129(to)002:1613: jo bo lang lab ni sku gzhon nu nas pha ma grongs /
NK129(to)002:1614: pha spun rnams kyi pha ma'i kha chems la ma nyan te /
NK129(to)002:1615: lang lab ma bu la khang pa smig gu gang dang /
NK129(to)002:1616: zhing chung gcig las ma byin pas /
NK129(to)002:1617: ngam bre sa les thugs kyi ma bzod nas /
NK129(to)002:1618: khyad par 'phags pa phur pa'i gdams pa 'di gnang ste /
NK129(to)002:1619: lang lab kyis sgrub pa byas te dgra thams cad tshar bcad /
NK129(to)002:1620: snyan grags kyi phyogs kun tu khyab kyang sbyin 'bras chung par 'phongs te /
NK129(to)002:1621: 'khon re na lug rdzi byed cing yod tsa na /
NK129(to)002:1622: de dus dge bshes r+aa lo tsa ba rdo rje grags sku bsod dang /
NK129(to)002:1623: mthu che bas bod kyi mi che dgu dang /
NK129(to)002:1624: bla ma slob dpon dge ba'i bshes gnyen thams cad
NK129(to)002:1625: kyis phyag dang zhe sa bkur sti 'bul dgos pa
NK129(to)002:1626: yin la / gal te ma byas na gshin rje'i
NK129(to)002:1627: gshed kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis skad cig la bsgrol
NK129(to)002:1628: yin la / ba yin te / khong la zhe sa ma byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1629: mar ba'i sras dar ma mdo sde la sogs pa
NK129(to)002:1630: sa thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' bcu gsum bsgral
NK129(to)002:1631: / gnyan lo ts+aa ba dar ma grags la sogs
NK129(to)002:1632: pa rang mnyam gyi lo ts+aa ba bcu gsum la
NK129(to)002:1633: sogs pa mang po bsgral ba'i yin cing /
NK129(to)002:1634: khong de tsa na grwa pa khri tshos skor te 'khor re ru chos 'khor la byon /
NK129(to)002:1635: 'khor re btsad po la sogs pas chos bzhi zla ba bzhi btegs /
NK129(to)002:1636: de dus r+aa lo tsa ba la lang lab kyis phyag ma btsal ba la /
NK129(to)002:1637: mi blun po zhig yin 'ong dgongs pa la /
NK129(to)002:1638: slar mi rnams kyis khong sku mthu che zhing phur pa la mkhas pa yin kyang /
NK129(to)002:1639: sku bsod chung pas da lta gzhan gyis lug rdzi byed dgos pa lags byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1640: 'o na kho nga rgyal gyi khong spos nas nga la phyag mi byed pa yin 'ong ste /
NK129(to)002:1641: kho la do nub kyi tshe las med kyi bsgur bsdod cig gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1643: rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi bsad pa'i sbyor ba bzhi'i bca' gzhi mdzad te /
NK129(to)002:1644: khyad par sbyin sreg gi skabs r+aa lo nyid rdo rje 'jigs byed dngos kyi skur gyur nas /
NK129(to)002:1645: ling ga la lang lab dgug bzhugs kyi bden brdar lan gsum byas te /
NK129(to)002:1646: dus der lang lab ni lug 'tsho ba nyid las gzhan ci yang mi byed mod kyi /
NK129(to)002:1647: dgug 'dren dang po'i dus der dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' skor na gnas pa'i rtsangs phur rnams byung ste /
NK129(to)002:1648: char du babs nas tho phyi'i grwa ba rnams smas /
NK129(to)002:1649: bar pa la za gsod dang khro bo bcu'i lcags
NK129(to)002:1650: phur gyis char babs nas 'khor rnams khyim gyi phug
NK129(to)002:1652: tha ma'i tshe nam mkha'i khams me dpung dang 'ur sgras gang ste /
NK129(to)002:1653: der steng du bltas pa na /
NK129(to)002:1654: rdo rje gzhon nu ri rdo chad tsam lcags bsregs las grub pa /
NK129(to)002:1655: stod khro bo smad phur pa /
NK129(to)002:1656: thugs kha nas phur pa drag tu bsgril shing /
NK129(to)002:1657: h'u phata kyi sgra sgrog pa zhig rwa lo ts+aa ba'i thog tu babs ma khad /
NK129(to)002:1658: za za rngam rngam 'cha' 'cha' ltar du 'dug pas rab tu skrag ste /
NK129(to)002:1659: de nyid du bzod par gsol /
NK129(to)002:1660: lang lab la gus 'dud byed par dam bcas pa dang cho 'phrul rnams yal song ngo //
NK129(to)002:1661: de nas de'i nub lang lab spyan drangs te /
NK129(to)002:1662: phyag dang zhe sa bsnyen bkur ba dang /
NK129(to)002:1664: dus der mi rnams na re /
NK129(to)002:1665: gshin rje mkhan po phur pa brdug /
NK129(to)002:1666: zhes pa'i gtam yang rgya cher grags skad /
NK129(to)002:1667: de lta bu'i slob dpon lang lab 'di bas lhag
NK129(to)002:1668: pa'i phur pa'i grub thob ni bod yul 'dir su
NK129(to)002:1670: slob ma yang kha yar byung zhing /
NK129(to)002:1671: mchog tu gyur pa ni bzhi yin te /
NK129(to)002:1672: 'khor re rgyal thang gi sna nam shes rab tshul khrims /
NK129(to)002:1674: rang gi skrangs phu ru mgo /'o yug rol po'i nyang nag dbang gi shes rab dang bzhi'o //
NK129(to)002:1675: nya nga nag gi bka' rkus /
NK129(to)002:1676: dbang dang gdams ngag med zer ba yang chags sdang gi gtam yin gyi /
NK129(to)002:1678: de ltar byin rlabs dang cho 'phrul phun sum tshogs
NK129(to)002:1679: pa phur pa'i chos 'di la dang po nyid nas
NK129(to)002:1680: / bdag cag gi bla ma'i bar du byin rlabs
NK129(to)002:1681: kyi rtags mtshan zam ma chad par byung ba yin
NK129(to)002:1682: / te / de yang slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis /
NK129(to)002:1683: rgya gar du tsan dan gyi nags la me shor
NK129(to)002:1684: te zhag mang por me ma shi nas nags tshal
NK129(to)002:1686: sems can mang po shi zhing la la shi la khad pa la /
NK129(to)002:1687: seng ldeng gi phur pa sor brgyad pa zhig btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1688: me shi ste nags tshal sngar las phun sum tshogs pa skyes /
NK129(to)002:1689: sems can shi ba dang shi la khad pa rnams gsos /
NK129(to)002:1690: tsan dan nags la thebs zer kyang //
NK129(to)002:1691: 'byung ba me la thebs pa yin /
NK129(to)002:1692: slob dpon 'di'i dben pa ni bal yul yang le shod kyi brag phug /
NK129(to)002:1693: slob dpon gyi gsang mtshan ni bde ba'i myu gu'o //
NK129(to)002:1694: slob dpon bi ma la mi tras chu bo gang g+aa la thebs te /
NK129(to)002:1695: slob dpon gyi chu bo gang g+aa'i 'gram du sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:1696: de'i sngags kyi zer phyogs de'i klu chen po gcig
NK129(to)002:1697: gis ma bzod nas phyi'i rgya mtsho chen po gnam
NK129(to)002:1698: du bcol / slob dpon la skyin thang drag po phab /
NK129(to)002:1699: chu bo gang g+aa lud te lung par mi shong par byas byung ba la /
NK129(to)002:1700: slob dpon gyis phur pa sor brgyad pa gcig btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1701: gang g+aa yar mar du chad de bar du lam dod te phyin chog pa byung /
NK129(to)002:1702: 'di ni gang g+aa la btab zer yang /
NK129(to)002:1705: bal po sh+ai la many+dzusa man+dala'i khar gong la thebs te /
NK129(to)002:1706: man+dala'i khar gong la brag srin mo gdug pa can
NK129(to)002:1707: zhig gnas pa des slob dpon gyi dgongs pa la
NK129(to)002:1709: phur pa bsgril bas man+dala'i khar gong gi brag nas sran tsam du nyil lo //
NK129(to)002:1710: 'di ni brag khar gong la thebs zer te /
NK129(to)002:1711: brag srin mo la thebs pa'o //
NK129(to)002:1712: lo rgyus gzhan dag na ni /
NK129(to)002:1713: rgya gar du phyi nang gnyis ma 'chams pa na rgyal pos zhag gsum na rtsod pa gyis zhig /
NK129(to)002:1714: su rgyal ba dang rdzu 'phrul su che ba de'i zhabs nas 'degs so zer /
NK129(to)002:1717: brjod rgyu thams cad tha snyad mtha' la gnas //
NK129(to)002:1718: don ma mthong bar grol ba ga la 'gyur //
NK129(to)002:1719: mu stegs 'chal ba'i gtam gyis ci zhig bya //
NK129(to)002:1720: chos kyi rgyal mtshan chen po 'dzugs par bya //
NK129(to)002:1721: zhes gsungs nas phur pa bsgril bas /
NK129(to)002:1722: man+da la zhes bya ba'i grong khyer chen po zhig
NK129(to)002:1723: gis rgyab na khar gong gi brag chen po zhig
NK129(to)002:1724: yod pa las / brag de nyid te mu stegs kyi grong khyer thams cad bcoms /
NK129(to)002:1725: mu stegs rnams la la khrag tu skyugs te shi /
NK129(to)002:1727: la la mig 'bras brul nas thams cad tshar bcad nas /
NK129(to)002:1728: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i bstan pa dar bar byas so //
NK129(to)002:1729: mkhas gong mthu yis bcad zhes grags /
NK129(to)002:1731: bod yul du byung ba ni /
NK129(to)002:1732: jo mo mkhar chen gza' mtsho rgyal gyi dben pa
NK129(to)002:1733: 'o yug mkhar ba sna ru mdzad pa'i dus su
NK129(to)002:1734: / byang phyogs kyi bye ma spyang ku 'dra ba la thebs /
NK129(to)002:1735: de yang byang phyogs na yar ldong ston gi tshong pa mang po yongs pa las /
NK129(to)002:1736: tshong dpon 'am tshong lha rgyal po shes ging gis byed pa las /
NK129(to)002:1738: byang spyang bcu bzhis rta bong rnams nyal bsad /
NK129(to)002:1739: tha ma mi la za ru byung ba las tshong pas lha 'dre'i bardzura yin pa shes te /
NK129(to)002:1740: yul na byin brlabs che ba su yod dris pas /
NK129(to)002:1741: mkhar ba sna na jo mo bzhugs zer te /
NK129(to)002:1742: der jo mo'i drung du phyin nas zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:1743: jo mos de rnams bstan pa mchod pa'i sbyin bdag yin par mkhyen nas /
NK129(to)002:1744: spyang ku rnams kyis rjes sa khyer shog gsungs pas /
NK129(to)002:1745: bye ma la rjes 'dug pa blangs te phul bas /
NK129(to)002:1746: jo mos rjes sa dang bag phye gzugs bcu bzhi byas nas phur pa btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1747: spyang ku bcu bzhi po dngos su mkhar ba sna'i
NK129(to)002:1748: gnya' na mar la hril li li 'dril nas lhung
NK129(to)002:1749: byung / spyang ku la thebs zer yang /
NK129(to)002:1750: rgyal po shes ging la thebs so //
NK129(to)002:1753: 'di'i slob ma me nub rgyal ba'i snying po yin te /
NK129(to)002:1754: 'di'i jo mo la dkor nor sna re la /
NK129(to)002:1755: nor sna khri tsho re ri ba bdun phul /
NK129(to)002:1756: dar gyi dge tsho'i steng nas jo mos bshad /
NK129(to)002:1757: mthing shog la gser gyis bris te gleg bam du byas /
NK129(to)002:1758: dben pa gar sha mkha' 'gro'i gling yin /
NK129(to)002:1762: de yang 'phreng ba na baza'i khar bzhag ste dbu
NK129(to)002:1763: skra bsil bas bya rog gi phreng ba khyer ba
NK129(to)002:1764: la / brtag pas bya rog bdud nag po bkrag
NK129(to)002:1765: med kyi sprul pas bar chod byed par mkhyen nas
NK129(to)002:1766: la / / bya rog gi grib ma la phur pa btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1767: bya rog sa la lhung nas shi'o //
NK129(to)002:1768: bya rog la thebs zer yang /
NK129(to)002:1770: de'i slob ma lo dpal gyi blo gros yin te /
NK129(to)002:1771: dben sa spa dro stag tshang seng ge phug /
NK129(to)002:1772: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal /
NK129(to)002:1774: de yang slob dpon mon na bzhugs dus dmag gis dgon pa bshig /
NK129(to)002:1776: de nas dgongs rgyud rtsa 'grel tsho bsnams te spa dro stag tshang du byon /
NK129(to)002:1777: bsnyen pa byas pas rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gzigs
NK129(to)002:1778: lho'i spa'i khyim la dmigs nas phur pa btab pas
NK129(to)002:1779: / dngos su spa khyim la phur pa bcur bcur
NK129(to)002:1780: byung nas mon pa rnams kyi snying la phur pa
NK129(to)002:1781: re thar thar zug nas kun bsgral lo //
NK129(to)002:1782: lho'i spa khyim la thebs zer yang /
NK129(to)002:1784: de'i slob ma ngam 'bre klu'i rgyal mtshan /
NK129(to)002:1785: dben pa nya stod srin mo ri'i co to /
NK129(to)002:1786: gsang mtshan bdud 'dul grags pa rtsal /
NK129(to)002:1787: dgra la btabs pas bgegs la thebs /
NK129(to)002:1788: de yang slob dpon 'dis phur pa 'grub pas dgra bgegs gnyis la ngang ngam shugs kyi thebs /
NK129(to)002:1789: nyon mongs pa dug lnga la thebs te lta dgongs phul du phyin /
NK129(to)002:1790: bar chad dgra bgegs thams cad bsgral nas /
NK129(to)002:1791: dgung lo dgu bcu rtsa dgu la sku 'das te /
NK129(to)002:1792: spur sbyangs pas gdung rus ci yang ma byung ste /
NK129(to)002:1793: rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku zhal gsum phyag drug pa chag gang pa zhig dang /
NK129(to)002:1794: k+ai l+aa ya 'bur dod cig phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob pa'i rtags su byung ngo //
NK129(to)002:1795: de'i sras ngam 'bre sa le shes rab dbang phyug ste /
NK129(to)002:1796: 'dis bla ma la 'bul ba chen po byas te rma gtsang skyi gtsang gi 'gram du zhus /
NK129(to)002:1797: dben sa gong ma dang gcig la /
NK129(to)002:1798: gsang mtshan bgegs rigs 'joms pa rtsal /
NK129(to)002:1800: de yang srin mo rin sgrubs pa la bzhugs dus /
NK129(to)002:1801: nub gcig 'od chen po gcig byung /
NK129(to)002:1802: 'od de la phur pa btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1803: tho rangs mi dkar po gcig byung ba na re /
NK129(to)002:1804: slob dpon gyii bka' 'khor la gnod pa mi byed kyi /
NK129(to)002:1806: der kho la mna' 'gags nas phur pa bton te /
NK129(to)002:1809: bla ma 'di nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang chu
NK129(to)002:1810: la mi byings pa la sogs pa dngos grub du
NK129(to)002:1811: ma la dbang 'byor pa yin no //
NK129(to)002:1812: 'di'i slob ma lang lab rdo rje yin te /
NK129(to)002:1813: rma chu rab kyi pha rol skyi chu rab kyi tshu rol /
NK129(to)002:1815: phyis gser srang brgyad cu las byas pa'i 'jam dpal gyi sku gcig phul /
NK129(to)002:1816: de sna drangs te nor sna bdun phul /
NK129(to)002:1817: lang lab kyi dben pa 'khor re'i rdo rje rtse 'dus /
NK129(to)002:1818: gsang mtshan phrin las mthar phyin rtsal /
NK129(to)002:1819: 'dis spyir dgra bgegs kun la thebs /
NK129(to)002:1820: lang lab kyi nor rku la shor ba las /
NK129(to)002:1821: rkun ma'i rjes sa la phur pa btabs /
NK129(to)002:1822: 'bre grags po bya ba zhag gsum na shi ste /
NK129(to)002:1823: shul mi rnams kyis nor skyal lo //
NK129(to)002:1824: slob dpon 'dis sgrub pa mdzad pa la phur pa rnams 'phar ba dang 'phyongs pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1825: me dang du ma la sogs pa byung /
NK129(to)002:1826: lcags phur gcig brag gis ngos la btab pa la
NK129(to)002:1827: phyugs rdzi dang shing 'thu ba dag gis lag pa
NK129(to)002:1828: 'jus te dpyangs la g.yug pa sogs rtsed mo byed
NK129(to)002:1829: pa byung ngo // 'di yan chod du phur pa chig brgyud yin no //
NK129(to)002:1830: 'di las gong du bstan pa ltar slob ma mang du byung la /
NK129(to)002:1832: sna snam shes tshul gyis thugs zin pas /
NK129(to)002:1833: phrin las dang lag len man ngag dril nas gnang /
NK129(to)002:1834: rgyud 'grel che ba rnams ma gnang la /
NK129(to)002:1835: rtsa ba'i rgyud rdo rje khros pa'i dum bu gnang /
NK129(to)002:1836: 'di rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma yin zer /
NK129(to)002:1837: man ngag 'phrin las bzhi'i don 'di la gnang ba rnams shin du zab par byed do //
NK129(to)002:1839: yul mi rnams kyis nor phyugs khang zhing thams cad phrog pa la bsten nas /
NK129(to)002:1840: lang lab kyi rtsa ra byon nas gdams pa zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:1841: zla ba dgu lha bsnyen gyis la /
NK129(to)002:1842: de nas bse lcags shel gsum la zla ba gnyis sgrubs shig /
NK129(to)002:1844: de ltar sgrubs pas lung drod tshad du phyin /
NK129(to)002:1845: de nas gyang gi drung na mi mang po nyi
NK129(to)002:1846: ma la 'ong zhing 'dug pas thams cad dgra ru
NK129(to)002:1848: gong khug nas phur pa phyungs te gyang la btab pas /
NK129(to)002:1849: gyang 'gyel ba'i thib 'og tu mi kun shi bas /
NK129(to)002:1850: skyi nag gyang bsgyel du grags /
NK129(to)002:1851: gyang la thebs zer yang dgra la thebs /
NK129(to)002:1852: 'di shes rab che bas rgyud 'grel man ngag thams cad gnang ngo //
NK129(to)002:1854: sngar nas phur pa mang po shes /
NK129(to)002:1856: 'dis kun kha mthun par jo mo mkhar chen baza'i
NK129(to)002:1857: thugs dam gyi phur pa jo bo lang lab la
NK129(to)002:1858: yod zer bas / nas bong khal drug /
NK129(to)002:1861: chang rkyal pa gang rnams khyer te 'kho rer 'ongs /
NK129(to)002:1862: der lang lab bza' mi gnyis la sras ni mi mnga'/
NK129(to)002:1863: nor rdzas srab mo las med las /
NK129(to)002:1865: shing cha btsongs nas za ba las /
NK129(to)002:1866: sprang phu ru mgo bong khal ded nas phyi sgo
NK129(to)002:1867: med pas khang pa'i nang du btsangs kyis byung ba
NK129(to)002:1868: dang / lang lab kyis jo bo sngags pa ni
NK129(to)002:1869: mgron khang ma lags sgo nor ba ma yin nam
NK129(to)002:1872: ma lags 'di khar chos kyi bka' drin zhur mchis pa lags /
NK129(to)002:1873: zer nas khal tsho phog zhes sa phul /
NK129(to)002:1874: gtam mthun sbyor mang po btang /
NK129(to)002:1877: nas phul nas phur pa jo mo zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1878: da 'o na zla ba phyed nas shes par bya gsungs nas gnang ste /
NK129(to)002:1879: dpa' bo gcig par sgrub pa'i don zab du gnang ngo //
NK129(to)002:1880: de sras sprang gyis rong du slob ma mang du bsdus /
NK129(to)002:1881: khong rang gi phur pa gcig brgyud mang po shes pas /
NK129(to)002:1882: de tsho nas btus kyin sgrubs thabs mang du brtsams /
NK129(to)002:1883: 'di jo mo mkhar chen gaza'i thugs dam yin /
NK129(to)002:1884: lang lab byang chub rdo rje'i phyag nas 'ongs zer zhing /
NK129(to)002:1885: slob ma rnams la so sor mi 'dra ba mang po bstan pas /
NK129(to)002:1886: phur ba rtsa dum gyis chos skor 'chal mgo zug /
NK129(to)002:1887: so sor mi 'dra ba mang bas sprang kyi slob
NK129(to)002:1888: ma rnams kyang nga'i 'di jo mo lugs yin zer
NK129(to)002:1889: cing gcig la gcig mi mgu /
NK129(to)002:1890: da lta jo mo lugs kyi sgrubs thabs mi 'dra ba mang po byung ba yang de yin /
NK129(to)002:1892: bdag gis ni sprang kyis byas pa'i yi cha ma
NK129(to)002:1893: mthong bas 'thad mi 'thad spro bas mi nus so
NK129(to)002:1894: // da ni slob ma bzhi pa nyang nag dbang
NK129(to)002:1895: gi shes rab kyis lo rgyus brjod par bya ste
NK129(to)002:1896: // / de yang lang lab yab yum gnyis zas nor gyi 'phongs par yod pa la /
NK129(to)002:1897: nyang nag gi 'o yug rol por gong mar spyan drangs zhabs tog byas /
NK129(to)002:1898: der lo gsum song ba dang /
NK129(to)002:1899: jo mo de khar bzhag nas /
NK129(to)002:1900: slob dpon ldong kha smad na mar snyed pa tshol
NK129(to)002:1901: bar byon nas zla ba dgu'i bar du ma byon
NK129(to)002:1902: / der jo mo skyo zhing yid chad nas /
NK129(to)002:1903: nang ma zhig jo mos nyang nag bos nas /
NK129(to)002:1904: slob dpon 'di bas snying thag rang ba ma byung gi /
NK129(to)002:1905: khyed rang chos 'dod na ngas sbyin no zer /
NK129(to)002:1906: 'o na dang bdag daga'o byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1907: 'o na sgro ba nag po 'di kha phye zhig zer nas /
NK129(to)002:1908: slob dpon lang lab kyis la rgya yod pa bcag nas kha phye /
NK129(to)002:1909: dbang ma thob pa la dgongs brgyud bris pas /
NK129(to)002:1910: nyang nag la bkra mi shis pa byung ste /
NK129(to)002:1911: gnag phyugs mang po yod pa la gnag nad byung ste /
NK129(to)002:1915: slob dpon gshegs pa'i phyogs kyi ri mtho sar phyin
NK129(to)002:1916: te gtor tshogs mang po bshams nas bshags pa byas
NK129(to)002:1917: / slob dpon spyan drangs nas nor rdzas kyi phyed 'bul ba byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1918: gnag nad dang bkra mi shis pa kun chad /
NK129(to)002:1919: slob dpon spyan 'dren pa btang ngo //
NK129(to)002:1920: der slob dpon byon pa dang /
NK129(to)002:1921: sngar jo mos gsungs pa la sogs pa'i lo rgyus bsnyad pas /
NK129(to)002:1922: slob dpon na re e he he lha'i khug mar srin gyi lag pa bardzangasa ang gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1923: der gong gis dam bcas pa'i nor rdzas tsho phul nas chos zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1925: 'o na sngon la khyed pha spad dbang zhig thob pa bya dgos gsungs nas /
NK129(to)002:1926: yab sras gsum la chos kyi dbang rdzogs bar bskur te /
NK129(to)002:1927: 'di ltar dbang phyi nang gsang gsum bskur ro //
NK129(to)002:1928: der sras che ba de sngar bu yin pas yab dang ma yar sdang zhing dbang chung bar 'dug /
NK129(to)002:1929: bu chung ba ni gces phrug byed de de'i ming tshu le zer ba yin /
NK129(to)002:1930: che ba la gnang nge zer te 'di rig pa can sngags kyi snod dang ldan par gzigs nas /
NK129(to)002:1931: lang lab kyis ming spos nas /
NK129(to)002:1933: de nas slob dpon lang lab kyi zhal nas /
NK129(to)002:1934: nges rgas 'khogs gnyis kyis nor 'di tsho'i nyar ra mi yongs ba gda' yi /
NK129(to)002:1935: 'di tsho khyed rang yab sras mdzod lags /
NK129(to)002:1936: nged mi gnyis ma shi bar du mi sdug pa zhig zhu gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1937: der nyang nag dbang gi shes rab thugs ma bde ste /
NK129(to)002:1938: slob dpon khyad par can 'di la gdung brgyud cig byung na bstan pa dang sems can la'ang phan /
NK129(to)002:1939: nga'i bu tsha rgyud rnams kyis phyag mchod pa 'bul sa zhig kyang dgos pa 'dug snyam nas /
NK129(to)002:1940: jo mo bgres mo lo lnga bcu lnga brgyad lon pa de la rgyu mtshan smras te /
NK129(to)002:1941: nga la bsam mno' 'di 'dra cig bdog /
NK129(to)002:1942: nor rdzas 'di tsho'i bdag po gcig kyang dgos pa
NK129(to)002:1943: gda' bas jo mo zhig blang na rung ngam byas
NK129(to)002:1944: pas / jo mos de shin tu legs so gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1945: de nas slob dpon la zhus pas mi byed gsung /
NK129(to)002:1946: der gong gi rgyu mtshan tsho zhib tu brjod te /
NK129(to)002:1947: jo mos ni gnang lags byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1948: rgan mo la mi dga' ba mi 'dug gam gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1949: jo mo dges pa gda' lags zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:1950: 'o na bya na yang bya gsung /
NK129(to)002:1951: der rus 'o phya bza' yin pa'i bu mo zhig blang nas /
NK129(to)002:1952: jo mo la phul bas sras gnyis byung ste /
NK129(to)002:1953: che ba la grags chung zer /
NK129(to)002:1954: nu bo la grags pa dbang phyug tu btags /
NK129(to)002:1955: de tsa na nyang nag dbang gi shes rab kyi chos thams cad khongs su chud /
NK129(to)002:1956: bla ma yab yum gyi zhabs tog kyang 'di nyid kho na bzang ba yin no //
NK129(to)002:1957: de nas skabs shig tu nyang nag shog gu mang po sbyar nas yod pa la /
NK129(to)002:1960: rgyud 'grel zhal bshu pa lags byas pas slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK129(to)002:1961: bdag ni nyi ma rgas kha 'dra /
NK129(to)002:1962: chos kyi bdag po nyid lags kyis /
NK129(to)002:1963: bla dpe zhal ma bshu bar tshags mdzod cig gsung /
NK129(to)002:1964: bla dpe sras gnyis la dgos mod byas pas /
NK129(to)002:1965: byis pa gnyis gsang sngags kyi snod du rung zhing mthar phyin pa'i nges pa med /
NK129(to)002:1966: de ltar byung na de dus gdams pa phyin pas chog mod gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1967: bla dpe' po sti bse gleg can bya ba /
NK129(to)002:1968: dgongs rgyud kyi gleg shing la bse'i lha mo bzhi bris pa'i po sti gnang ngo //
NK129(to)002:1970: nyang ro kho re ru lang lab byang chub rdo rje rabs chad /
NK129(to)002:1971: 'o yug phu ru sras gnyis skyes /
NK129(to)002:1973: phyis sras gnyis po chos par ma song /
NK129(to)002:1974: phyugs po chen po gnyis byung /
NK129(to)002:1975: grags chung la bu gnyis la che ba yon bdag ldeng rtse /
NK129(to)002:1976: 'dis gsungs rab mang po bzhengs so //
NK129(to)002:1978: jo mos la rgya bcag ba'i gtam 'di la bsnyon te /
NK129(to)002:1981: sprang gsum nyang nag gis bka' rkus zer te /
NK129(to)002:1982: phyis nyang nag sras kyi thu bor gyur pa yin no //
NK129(to)002:1983: byin rlabs dang nus mthu yang phul du byung ba'i gtam rgyus mang la /
NK129(to)002:1984: dben pa ni 'o yug sgo mo'i skam ma skam
NK129(to)002:1985: gyi brag phug zer rgyab snyam bzang gi brag phug
NK129(to)002:1986: tu'o // gsang mtshan rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal /
NK129(to)002:1987: snyam bzang phug par sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:1988: phur pa nam mkha' la lding ba dang /
NK129(to)002:1989: 'od dang sgra dang bcas pa byung /
NK129(to)002:1990: dgra bgegs thams cad btul ba yin no /
NK129(to)002:1991: 'dis dgung lo brgya bcu rtsa lnga bzhes nas 'da' khar sras tshul le la zhal chems gsungs pa /
NK129(to)002:1992: sh+aakya rgyal mtshan gyis ni man ngag thams cad shes /
NK129(to)002:1993: khos dpe' cha kun khyer ba 'ong ngo //
NK129(to)002:1994: 'og khang gi ka zhu'i kha na po sti bse gleg can yod do //
NK129(to)002:1995: bu rang tshags kyis la spos zhig gsungs /
NK129(to)002:1996: der 'og khang na sh+aakya rgyal mtshan yod pas tshor te /
NK129(to)002:1997: yid chad nas po sti bse gleg can yod pa
NK129(to)002:1998: khyer nas bros phyin snye bu'i gnas bya ba la
NK129(to)002:1999: yab kyi slob ma gnang h'u ka ra bya ba
NK129(to)002:2000: zhig yod pa de'i sar phyin te /
NK129(to)002:2001: yab ni grongs su cha ba yod /
NK129(to)002:2002: tshul le la zhal chems gsungs /
NK129(to)002:2003: yid chad pa'i tshul smras pas /
NK129(to)002:2004: gnang h'u ka ra ha las te /
NK129(to)002:2005: slob dpon grongs su cha na /
NK129(to)002:2006: po sti khyer nas bros pas dam tshig nyams nas 'gro bas /
NK129(to)002:2007: nang par rang re gnyis ga 'dengs /
NK129(to)002:2008: chos nu bo la yang sbyin dgos zer /
NK129(to)002:2009: nang par phyin tsa na yab grong nas 'dug /
NK129(to)002:2010: der gnang h'u ka ras spun gnyis mthun par byas so //
NK129(to)002:2011: de nas dus re zhig na bshags pa mang po byas /
NK129(to)002:2012: tshogs kyi 'khor lo mang po bskor /
NK129(to)002:2013: de nas dben pa ru mchod gnyis kyi bsnyen bsgrub
NK129(to)002:2014: mdzad pas rtags dang mtshan ma mang po ni byung
NK129(to)002:2015: / nub cig mar me mi gsal /
NK129(to)002:2016: sgra snyan mang po grags pa dang /
NK129(to)002:2017: sh+aakya rgyal mtshan spyan mi gsal bas /
NK129(to)002:2018: tshul le la mar me de chos dang gsung /
NK129(to)002:2019: tshul les mar me bcos par phyin pas sgra snyan mang po thos shing /
NK129(to)002:2020: dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i lha phur tsho bro pa
NK129(to)002:2021: do rar zhugs pa bzhin cod pan zing zing 'khrab
NK129(to)002:2023: gcen la 'di ltar brda' byas pas /
NK129(to)002:2025: zang nag chen po zhig bsnam nas /
NK129(to)002:2026: phyag tu sba 'khar dngul mgo can bsnams nas sa la btsugs te /
NK129(to)002:2027: mched gnyis kyis bstod pa mdzad de dngos grub blangs so //
NK129(to)002:2029: slob dpon sh+aakya rgyal mtshan gyis tshong pa mang po'i dpon mdzad de ldong kha na phar byon pas /
NK129(to)002:2030: 'dar nag po'i rta pa nyi shu rtsa gcig gis tshong pa thams cad bcoms /
NK129(to)002:2031: der stir ris gshegs nas gzigs pas nom pa bgo ba mthong nas ber sngon po de phud nas /
NK129(to)002:2032: lha bos klu bos nas brdab pas /
NK129(to)002:2033: mi rgan zhig gdong du byung nas /
NK129(to)002:2034: lung pa 'di sa gnyan rdo gnyan /
NK129(to)002:2037: mi rung ba kho na 'dod gsungs /
NK129(to)002:2038: de'i nub mo mi nyal tsam pa'i dus tshod la
NK129(to)002:2039: cong dings pa zhig byung nas rta pa gsum shar
NK129(to)002:2040: song / nang par nyan tsa na tshong dpon gyi
NK129(to)002:2041: bu'i mgo la slob dpon gyi rta yis 'khra rgyab
NK129(to)002:2042: ste shi ru cha zer skad der slob dpon 'khor
NK129(to)002:2043: bcas gyis nub mo bros nas phyin /
NK129(to)002:2044: phyi de lo dus na rta pa bcu dgu shi'o //
NK129(to)002:2045: gnyis kyi dpon slob can du 'ongs nas 'bangs byas so //
NK129(to)002:2046: der nyang nag ber sngon can zhes phyogs kun tu grags so //
NK129(to)002:2047: dben pa mnyam mnyam brag phug /
NK129(to)002:2048: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde chen rtsa la /
NK129(to)002:2049: thebs pa zhang po nyang nag la thebs /
NK129(to)002:2050: de yang snub yul rong gi sa'i cha 'grogs bya bar 'khrungs /
NK129(to)002:2051: mi mang po nye res med pa zhig yin /
NK129(to)002:2052: chung ngu la pha ma shi nas /
NK129(to)002:2053: zhang po nyang nag gis ris bin+d+ha 'phen po mang
NK129(to)002:2054: po yod pas de rnams kyi nor rdzas thams cad
NK129(to)002:2055: phrog nas sprang du btang ngo //
NK129(to)002:2056: der slob dpon sh+aakya rgyal mtshan dang mjal /
NK129(to)002:2057: lo bco brgyad nas sum cu'i bar du bla ma'i snag rdzi'u byas /
NK129(to)002:2058: bla mas gsang sngags kyi snod du rung bar gzigs /
NK129(to)002:2059: shes rab che bas phyugs skyong rin la man ngag thams cad gnang /
NK129(to)002:2060: phyag bzhes thams cad la mkhas pa'i phul du phyin /
NK129(to)002:2062: da ni ngas kyang lo brgyad cu gya lnga lon snang ba yal las su chod /
NK129(to)002:2064: der slob dpon drag po la yul na nor bag tsam yod pas der bri ba'am zhus pas /
NK129(to)002:2065: legs kyi 'dir bu gnyis po phrag dog skyes pa srid do gsungs /
NK129(to)002:2066: der po sti kun gnang nas yul du 'dri yin yod tsa na /
NK129(to)002:2067: slob dpon gyi sras che ba chos tshul bya ba byon nas /
NK129(to)002:2068: a po drag po yab ni grongs nas med /
NK129(to)002:2069: pi sti bse gleg can yang mi 'dug /
NK129(to)002:2070: de su la 'dug pa zhig la mgo bskyel ba la zer /
NK129(to)002:2071: slob dpon grongs nas mi dga' ha las pa'i steng du /
NK129(to)002:2072: spo sti bse gleg can su 'dug pa la mgo bskyel zer bas yang dang yang du ma dga'/
NK129(to)002:2073: po sti nga la yod zer ni ma phod /
NK129(to)002:2074: der bla dpe slob dpon drag po la lus so //
NK129(to)002:2075: de tsa na bla ma drag po'i zhang po nor
NK129(to)002:2076: 'phrog mi kun gyis slar yang 'di nyang nag ber
NK129(to)002:2077: sngon can gyis mthus snyem pa yin nam /
NK129(to)002:2079: ci nus pa rems zhig zer kha smras byed do //
NK129(to)002:2080: de nas slob dpon gyis lhan du byon te /
NK129(to)002:2081: bud med cig la yul zhig brten thub tsam gcig 'dug pas /
NK129(to)002:2083: der lhan gyi stag lung grog por dben pa byas
NK129(to)002:2084: te sgrub pa mdzad pas rtags mtshan mang du byung
NK129(to)002:2085: / zhang po dregs pa can de kun gyis 'dums byed du ni ma 'dod pa'i khar /
NK129(to)002:2086: zla ba ga cig na slob dpon drag po mthus bsgang gis btang gi zer /
NK129(to)002:2087: g.yas ru gtsang po'i rtsa ba na brag phug yod
NK129(to)002:2088: pa der nyang nag ben+d+ha bcu gsum zhugs nas mthu
NK129(to)002:2089: byed do // slob dpon gyis kyang stag lung grog por drag las byas pas /
NK129(to)002:2090: de nas zla ba gsum na nyang nag ben+d+ha bcu gsum po la glo tsha thebs nas kun shi'o //
NK129(to)002:2091: phyis 'grogs lung par ltad mo chen po zhig byung ba la /
NK129(to)002:2092: slob dpon drag pos zang nag chen po gcig gyon /
NK129(to)002:2094: 'khor mang pos bskor te ltad mo la byon pas /
NK129(to)002:2095: zhang ne mo kun gyis sa gtor te /
NK129(to)002:2096: zhang mi thong po ngan pa byung ngo zer zhing 'a tsi 'a tsi zer ba la /
NK129(to)002:2098: 'a tsi bya ba khyod rang yin mod /
NK129(to)002:2100: bar du zlum mi byed par mthu byed /
NK129(to)002:2101: tha ma ben+d+ha bcu gsum srog dang bral nas phung /
NK129(to)002:2102: 'a tsi bya ba khyed rang tsho yin mod zer zhing ya ga bsgrags so //
NK129(to)002:2103: slob dpon drag po 'dis dgongs brgyud skor la mi mkhyen pa med cing /
NK129(to)002:2104: mthu dang sku bsod che bas dbus gtsang gis mkhas btsun thams cad kyi zhabs la gtugs so //
NK129(to)002:2105: 'di mar pa lo ts+aa ba dang dus mtshungs pa yin /
NK129(to)002:2106: de tsa na sna snam shes rab tshul khrims la
NK129(to)002:2107: sras gnyis yod pa'i che ba sna snam 'bro ban
NK129(to)002:2108: la sku dgra zhig byung nas /
NK129(to)002:2109: dgra de dag gi mthu zlog pa la snubs zam nag stod pa'i /
NK129(to)002:2110: jo bo stag ram spyan drangs so //
NK129(to)002:2111: lan cig sna snam 'bro ban dang /
NK129(to)002:2112: snubs stags ram zam kha gcig tu mjal ba dang /
NK129(to)002:2113: sna snam gyis jo bo stag ram la phyag byas te /
NK129(to)002:2115: mi 'di pas bdag la mi mtshams pa'i las mang po bgyis pas /
NK129(to)002:2116: thugs dam la dgongs la 'di pa'i bsrungs pa mdzad par zhu byas pas /
NK129(to)002:2117: snubs stag ram gyi zhal nas /
NK129(to)002:2118: lang lab byang chub rdo rje'i phur thung res sbos pa /
NK129(to)002:2121: sna snams khros nas gos nag brdabs /
NK129(to)002:2122: ngas ma nyes ma yo'o byas so //
NK129(to)002:2124: gnyis ga phug tu zhugs pas /
NK129(to)002:2125: zla ba gsum na snubs stag ram khrag skyugs te shi'o //
NK129(to)002:2126: gshin rje mkhan po phur pa la rdugs bya ba dus der yang grags la /
NK129(to)002:2127: der sna snam gyis chang mang po btsos te /
NK129(to)002:2128: nyang ro'i ben+d+ha phur pa shes zer tshad spyan drangs te tshogs 'khor byas so //
NK129(to)002:2131: rdo rje gzhon nu'i gzhu mo la //
NK129(to)002:2133: khro bo pha bcu'i mda' smyug la //
NK129(to)002:2134: khro mo ma bcu'i sgro yis sgron //
NK129(to)002:2135: phur pa sras mchog gi made'u bcag /
NK129(to)002:2136: dam can rnam gsum gyis rgyus pas dkris //
NK129(to)002:2137: bse lcags shel gsum gyis ngar zhig blud //
NK129(to)002:2138: 'phangs ni zang nag gi phyogs su 'phangs //
NK129(to)002:2139: phog pa jo bo ltag ral la phog /
NK129(to)002:2140: mda' tshabs mi chung che bar gda' //
NK129(to)002:2142: des nas dar chos par phur pa rtsa dum 'chal chos te /
NK129(to)002:2143: nyang ro'i rgyal khams rtsam du lod //
NK129(to)002:2145: bdag cag la ni cha med lags /
NK129(to)002:2146: de ji ltar las chad pa na sna snam shes
NK129(to)002:2147: tshul gyis slob ma rgya ston sangs rgyas bya bas
NK129(to)002:2148: / shang kyi lung par phur pa rgyud 'grel gzhan
NK129(to)002:2149: nas bkab nas phur pa rtsa dum la brten pa'i
NK129(to)002:2151: jo mo mkhar chen gaza'i gdams ngag can gyis bltas pa na bsres kyang ma 'dres skad do //
NK129(to)002:2152: gdams ngag dang mi ldan pas ni bsres pa dang bslad pa mi shes /
NK129(to)002:2153: rgya ston sangs rgyas kyi slob ma rgya rtsags shes
NK129(to)002:2154: rab rgyal mtshan gyis kyang rtsa dum gyi sgrub gzhung
NK129(to)002:2155: mang po brtsams / shangs pa dgon ston gyis kyang brtsams /
NK129(to)002:2156: de'i slob ma sgro ston dar gtsug gis kyang sgrubs thabs mang du byas /
NK129(to)002:2157: la la gsang skor gyi slad /
NK129(to)002:2158: la la mdo skor gyi slad /
NK129(to)002:2159: de dag gi sgrubs thabs kyi ming ni man ngag drug pa dang /
NK129(to)002:2162: skyed pa sku'i thebs yig dang /
NK129(to)002:2166: phur pa 'dul bzhi la sogs pa mtshan gyis rnam grangs mang po btags skad /
NK129(to)002:2167: dus de tsa na jo bo ston pa kun na re /
NK129(to)002:2168: nga'i 'di jo mo mkhar chen gaza'i thugs dam yin /
NK129(to)002:2169: gzhan ma yin zer zhing gcig la gcig mi mgu skad /
NK129(to)002:2170: spyir dang por sprang phur ru 'gos /
NK129(to)002:2172: bar du rgya ston sangs rgyas la sogs pas shangs lung par gzhung mang po brtsams /
NK129(to)002:2173: tha mar gang zag shes rab can rnams kyis legs su re mang po re byas /
NK129(to)002:2174: ming phur pa rtsa dum du btags nas mi 'dra ba grangs las 'das /
NK129(to)002:2175: bka' dang brgyud pa man ngag ma chad pa chos
NK129(to)002:2176: ma slad pa man ngag thob pa gcig gis bltas
NK129(to)002:2178: bod du 'gyur ba'i chos la phur pa rtsa dum 'chal che skad /
NK129(to)002:2179: phur pa rtsa dum lhad med yod pa slob dpon drag po yin /
NK129(to)002:2182: gong gi de dag la lang lab kyi khyad chos
NK129(to)002:2183: jo mo mkhar chen gaza'i thugs tig 'di ma grags
NK129(to)002:2184: pa yin gyi / de dag gi brgyud pa rnams
NK129(to)002:2185: la gang zag bzang po sha stag byon pa yin
NK129(to)002:2186: pa yin gyi / pas / rang rang gi sgrub
NK129(to)002:2187: gzhung de dag pa 'chal ba'i skyon yod par mi
NK129(to)002:2188: pa yin gyi / pas / sems la / yang
NK129(to)002:2189: sgrubs thabs kha cig ni sbyor dngos rjes gsum ma
NK129(to)002:2190: pa yin gyi / pas / sems la / tshang pa dang / ma 'grel ba dang /
NK129(to)002:2191: nor ba la sogs pa kha yar snang lod kyi /
NK129(to)002:2192: deng sang ni nub nas nyams len byed par mi 'dug pas /
NK129(to)002:2193: zhib tu bri ma dgos so //
NK129(to)002:2194: slob dpon drag po la slob ma mang yang /
NK129(to)002:2195: thugs kyi sras su gyur pa ni gnyis yin te /
NK129(to)002:2196: byang ro rgyan khar gyi so ston khri rgyal dang /
NK129(to)002:2197: nyang stod kyi lce ston sh+aakya rgyal mtshan gnyis so //
NK129(to)002:2198: de la lce ston sh+aakya rgyal mtshan ni ston pa chen po zhig yin pas /
NK129(to)002:2199: 'khor mang pos bskor te gdug spur re byon te /
NK129(to)002:2200: slob dpon drag po mjal bas mkhyen pa la thugs
NK129(to)002:2201: mnyes nas rgyud 'grel thams cad gnang kyang ston pa
NK129(to)002:2202: 'di sku bsod che bas lag len ma lobs te
NK129(to)002:2203: mi mkhas / rgyud 'grel gyi bshad pa ni mkhas so //
NK129(to)002:2204: phyis lag len dang man ngag zhu bsam ste byon
NK129(to)002:2205: tsa na slob dpon drag po ni grongs nas mi
NK129(to)002:2206: bzhugs / slob dpon gyi jo mo skyi gu rang
NK129(to)002:2207: gi yul spyan drangs nas dbyangs tsho chod tsam byung
NK129(to)002:2208: bzhugs / / man ngag gi brgyud pa ma zin no //
NK129(to)002:2209: lce ston gyi slob ma skye chung ba shes rab
NK129(to)002:2210: grags bya ba shes rab can zhig gis dgongs brgyud
NK129(to)002:2211: bcos nas la stod du mang po la spel /
NK129(to)002:2212: 'go ba bya spel kyang rgyud la bcos skad /
NK129(to)002:2213: der dgongs rgyud la gnyis byung /
NK129(to)002:2214: skyi ston gyis man ngag med par rgyud 'grel gzhan gyis bslad nas mang du bshad do //
NK129(to)002:2215: slob dpon drag po'i chos rgyud zin pa'i slob ma ni so ston khri rgyal kho na yin te /
NK129(to)002:2216: rgyud 'grel man ngag kun la mkhas /
NK129(to)002:2217: dben pa rgyan mkhar gyis ngo dmar brag phug /
NK129(to)002:2218: gsang mtshan rdo rje gter sgrub rtsal /
NK129(to)002:2219: rtags dang mtshan ma phul du phyin /
NK129(to)002:2220: phur ba dgra bgegs gnyis la thebs so //
NK129(to)002:2221: 'di'i slob ma lha rje phur ston ring mo yin te /
NK129(to)002:2222: zhabs tog gis bla ma mnyes pa mang po mdzad te gdams pas ma lus pa thob /
NK129(to)002:2223: sku gzhon nu'i tshe slob dpon drag po la yang rtsa ba tshar gnyis zhus /
NK129(to)002:2224: dben pa khra ri'i rdo rje gnam rdzongs /
NK129(to)002:2225: gsang mtshan rdo rje las rab rtsal /
NK129(to)002:2228: bka' shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sras
NK129(to)002:2229: yum bcu bdun bzhengs pa la sogs dge ba'i las
NK129(to)002:2230: rgya cher mdzad / khra ri gnam rdzong bya ba
NK129(to)002:2231: de la stod rgyal gyis rtsibs ri'i byang nas rgyang
NK129(to)002:2232: tsam song pa'i ri la brag seng ge gnam du
NK129(to)002:2234: de'i steng na rdzong bar snang la ldeng nge ba 'dra ba zhig yod /
NK129(to)002:2235: de ru sgrubs pas rtags dang mtshan ma thob bo //
NK129(to)002:2236: de'i slob ma rgya ston nam mkha' rgyal pos khra
NK129(to)002:2237: ri gnam rdzong du bla ma mnyes par byas nas
NK129(to)002:2238: gdams pa man ngag tshang bar zhus kyang dbang ma
NK129(to)002:2239: thob pas / phyis rang gi gcen smyos ston nyi
NK129(to)002:2240: ma rdo rje bya ba lha rje phur gyis thugs
NK129(to)002:2241: thob pas / sras la zhus / dben pa ding
NK129(to)002:2242: ri srag nye'i bang steng dgon par bla ma smyos
NK129(to)002:2243: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / rgya
NK129(to)002:2244: ston gnyis kas sgrubs pas rtags dang mtshan ma mtha'
NK129(to)002:2245: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / ru
NK129(to)002:2246: phyin / gsang mtshan gnyis ka mthun pa rdo rje
NK129(to)002:2247: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / ru
NK129(to)002:2248: phyin / drag po rtsal / dgra bgegs gnyis ka
NK129(to)002:2249: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / ru
NK129(to)002:2250: phyin / drag po rtsal / la thebs / de
NK129(to)002:2251: ltar gnyis kas lha rje phur la thug kyang /
NK129(to)002:2253: lha rje smyos ston nyi ma rdo rje /
NK129(to)002:2254: rgya ston nam mkha' rgyal po zhes 'ded do //
NK129(to)002:2255: nam mkha' rgyal po'i slob ma rang gi sras gnyis las /
NK129(to)002:2256: sras chung pa nyi ma rgyal mtshan la rgyud 'grel gdams ngag tshang bar gnang /
NK129(to)002:2257: chung ngu nas yab kyi drung du phyag phyir lag len mang po mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:2258: lag len dbyangs dang bcas pa shin tu mkhas /
NK129(to)002:2259: yab kyis bsnyen sgrub la bcug pas rtags dang mtshan ma mang po brnyes /
NK129(to)002:2260: dgra bgegs gnyis ka la thebs /
NK129(to)002:2261: grub thob byin rlabs can du grags so //
NK129(to)002:2262: de'i slob ma nyang ban shu mang lung pa chen po yin te /
NK129(to)002:2263: bla ma la dbang rgyud 'grel man ngag tshang bar zhus /
NK129(to)002:2264: dben pa rong rgyan mkhar gyi thog phug /
NK129(to)002:2265: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang 'dus rtsal /
NK129(to)002:2267: de'i slo ma 'dzam gling pan+di ta nag po /
NK129(to)002:2268: 'di ni mi che bas nyang stod kyi bya chos
NK129(to)002:2269: mkhar po che la sogs pa mkhar gsum gyis bdag
NK129(to)002:2270: por gyur / rong du smugs bsam gling gi lha khang bzhengs /
NK129(to)002:2271: dben pa mon mo gtsug rum /
NK129(to)002:2272: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'dus pa rtsal /
NK129(to)002:2274: lha 'dre bran du 'khol ba la sogs pa'i yon tan mnga' lo //
NK129(to)002:2275: de'i slob ma shangs rdo rje gling pa bla chen rin po che yin te /
NK129(to)002:2276: 'di ni mkhas btsun bzang po'i yon tan du ma dang ldan /
NK129(to)002:2277: sku las tshul khrims kyi dri 'phro /
NK129(to)002:2278: bla ma 'jam gling pa rang gi dgon par spyan drangs nas dbang dang gdams pa zhus /
NK129(to)002:2281: de'i slob ma chu bar nyi phug pa chen po yin te /
NK129(to)002:2282: dben sa bres phu bsam gtan phug /
NK129(to)002:2283: gsang mtshan rdo rje thog 'bebs rtsal /
NK129(to)002:2286: de'i slob ma gtsang nya ri ban grong gi ston pa gsang sngags rdo rje yin te /
NK129(to)002:2287: dus phyis byin pa'i sngags pa rang la mkhyen pa dang nus mthu gnyis ga che /
NK129(to)002:2288: slob dpon pad+mas 'chims rdo rje spre'u chung gi skye bar lung bstan /
NK129(to)002:2289: bod la phan pa'i rten 'brel mang po byed dgos 'dug pas /
NK129(to)002:2290: mnga' ris rdzong kha'i chos rgyal gyi gdung rgyud rnams
NK129(to)002:2291: kyis mthun rkyen sbyar te sna 'ga' re yang grub
NK129(to)002:2292: / rdzong kha rgyal po'i sku rim gyi nub re'i
NK129(to)002:2293: thun gtor 'phangs pa'i tshe mtshan mo dngos su 'gro
NK129(to)002:2294: ba skye bo kun gyis mthun snang du grub pa
NK129(to)002:2295: sogs nus mthu'i grags pa thon /
NK129(to)002:2296: rdzong khar yi dam mang po'i zhal gzigs /
NK129(to)002:2297: 'dis sku gzhon nu'i dus su sgro sbug gi dben
NK129(to)002:2298: par phur pa'i sgrub pa zhag bdun mdzad pas rdo
NK129(to)002:2300: phur pa dgra bgegs gnyis ga la thebs so //
NK129(to)002:2301: de la mang yul skyi grong gi thugs rje chen
NK129(to)002:2302: po dang mtshungs pa 'phags pa wa ti bzhugs pa'i
NK129(to)002:2303: lha khang du / bdag cag gi bla ma dam
NK129(to)002:2304: pa grub pa'i dbang phyug chen po des gsan pa
NK129(to)002:2305: lha khang du / yin te / 'di ni chu
NK129(to)002:2306: pho rta'i lo la mi nyag 'ga' dang nye ba'i
NK129(to)002:2307: lha khang du / yin te / sar sku 'khrungs
NK129(to)002:2308: / dgung lo bco brgyad lon pa'i tshe sa g.yos
NK129(to)002:2309: kyi 'jigs pas nang mi dang grong pa kun shi
NK129(to)002:2310: bas thugs skyo ste dbus gtsang du chos la byon
NK129(to)002:2311: lha khang du / yin te / sar sku 'khrungs
NK129(to)002:2312: / / de nas yar lung btsan thang du gong
NK129(to)002:2313: ma grags pa 'byung gnas pas dmar ston rgyal mtshan
NK129(to)002:2315: btsan thang dbang mo cher grags pa'i chos 'khor bskor
NK129(to)002:2316: ba dang thugs te sngags gsar ma'i dbang bka' dang
NK129(to)002:2318: rje 'gos lo ts+aa ba la sbyor drug gi khrid
NK129(to)002:2319: gsan pas zla ba drug bsgoms pa la yon tan
NK129(to)002:2320: thams cad rdzogs par rje nyid shin tu dgyes te
NK129(to)002:2321: / khyod chos 'di la bag chags sad pa zhig 'dug gsungs /
NK129(to)002:2322: skabs der rdo rje'i zam pa gnang ba dang thugs
NK129(to)002:2323: pas rnying ma'i chos skor la dad pa 'chi ma
NK129(to)002:2325: chos thams cad thob pa zhig bya dgos snyam pa shar /
NK129(to)002:2327: dbu ru na zhogs thar pa gling bya ba na /
NK129(to)002:2328: sangs rgyas dbon po la yod zer /
NK129(to)002:2329: der byon te rdzogs pa chen po bka' gter phal cher gsan /
NK129(to)002:2330: 'bri khung du chos rje kun dga' rin chen la 'bri khung pa'i skor yongs rdzogs gsan /
NK129(to)002:2331: chos rje'i sku mdun du sang phu pa'i bka' bcu bstan gsal bya bas /
NK129(to)002:2332: dgong cig la dgag pa mang po byas pa la /
NK129(to)002:2333: lan btab pas chos rje dang bka' bcu gnyis ka dgyes /
NK129(to)002:2335: khams pa khyod 'di 'dra'i shes rab che ba lags mod /
NK129(to)002:2336: phyogs bslabs na sa skya pan+di ta 'dra ba zhig yod par 'dug zer /
NK129(to)002:2337: der ban dkar ba 'jam dpal bzang po'i 'bri gung du byon /
NK129(to)002:2338: khong la pan chen nags rin gyis chos skor zhus /
NK129(to)002:2340: khyod la bka' brgyud kyi bstan 'dzin zhig re bas stag lung du song gsung /
NK129(to)002:2342: stag lung ngag dbang grags pa la /
NK129(to)002:2343: bo dong pa'i chos bka' tsam las bka' brgyud ma thob kyang /
NK129(to)002:2344: lo bzhi bzhugs te thugs gtsigs che /
NK129(to)002:2345: slar 'bri khung du byon pa na chos rje gshegs /
NK129(to)002:2346: dpon po kun rin pa rten bzhengs kyi 'bul sdud
NK129(to)002:2347: la myong long la byon song 'dug pas yar klung
NK129(to)002:2348: du byon // 'on mthing ma sngags 'chang g.yu 'brug rdo rje la mdo dbang dang /
NK129(to)002:2350: de nas spa dro stag tshang du kahthoga pa ye shes 'bum pa la rgyud 'bum gyis lung dang /
NK129(to)002:2351: bka' ma'i chos bka' mang po zhus /
NK129(to)002:2352: rat+na gling pa'i dris lan mdzad kyi 'dug pas /
NK129(to)002:2353: de khyer nas lho brag shar du rat+na gling pa la phul /
NK129(to)002:2354: khong gi gter chos yongs rdzogs dang /
NK129(to)002:2356: phur pa bka' ma kha yar thob /
NK129(to)002:2357: de nas la stod byang du byon /
NK129(to)002:2358: brgya mkhar se ston pa la zhi khro phur gsum gyi skor dang /
NK129(to)002:2360: sgang shar sogs ma mo'i rgyud lung mang po dang /
NK129(to)002:2365: gshin rje dmar po la sogs pa khong la bzhugs tshad kyi chos gsan pas /
NK129(to)002:2366: po sti phyed dang sum brgya tsam gyis dbang lung thob /
NK129(to)002:2367: bla ma 'dis lto gos chos gsum ka gnang /
NK129(to)002:2368: lhag par bstan khur che ba'i 'di bas lhag pa'i bla ma med gsungs /
NK129(to)002:2369: lo rgyus gsung ba na'ang spyan chab 'byin /
NK129(to)002:2372: na ga ra ko ta la sogs pa'ang gzigs par byon /
NK129(to)002:2373: la stod lhor sngags 'chang nam bkras pa la bka' brgyad bka' gter mi gcig pa bdun dang /
NK129(to)002:2374: rdzogs chen a ro'i skor phal che ba dang /
NK129(to)002:2379: a ma na si ka ra'i skor /
NK129(to)002:2380: do ha mdzod 'jam dpal rdo rje'i skor la sogs pa mang po gsan /
NK129(to)002:2381: de nas yar klung su byon /
NK129(to)002:2382: khrus khang lo ts+aa ba la rngog dkyil bdun skor gsan /
NK129(to)002:2383: chags lo rin chen chos rgyal la lte'u ra ba'i
NK129(to)002:2384: chos rgyal la lte'u ra ba'i chos skor rdzogs pa
NK129(to)002:2385: dang / chos rje nam bkras pa la bka' gdams kyi skor mang po gsan /
NK129(to)002:2386: zhwa dmar ba bzhi pa la karma pa'i chos skor mtha' dag dang /
NK129(to)002:2387: yab tu byang sems chen po la zhi byed skor /
NK129(to)002:2388: gtsang smon pa la ras chung ba'i snyan rgyud la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK129(to)002:2389: zing pa stag mgor rgyal mtshan pa la kun mkhyen klong chen pa'i chos skor dang /
NK129(to)002:2390: dol pa sgrub chen ma la gcod yul dang /
NK129(to)002:2391: bla ma dgongs 'dus la sogs pa sangs rgyas gling pa'i chos skor ma lus pa dang /
NK129(to)002:2392: bsam gtan gling pa la khong ra'i a ti'i skor deng /
NK129(to)002:2393: sa skya bka' 'bum lam 'bras la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK129(to)002:2394: rgyal dbang chos rje kun dga' dpal 'byor ba la 'brug phyogs tha dag thob cing /
NK129(to)002:2395: shang 'ba' rar nam mkha' rgyal mtshan pa la stod
NK129(to)002:2396: 'brug dang bar 'brug dang 'bar chos mtha' dag dang
NK129(to)002:2397: / 'jags pa la shangs pa bka' brgyud skor dang /
NK129(to)002:2398: sku drung nyi zla ba la kun skyong gling pa'i chos skor dang /
NK129(to)002:2399: ngor du chos rje 'dren mchog la lam 'bras dang /
NK129(to)002:2401: zhwa lu ba dkon mchog bzang po la yo ga dang zhwa lu ba'i chos bka' phal cher gsan /
NK129(to)002:2402: chos rje byang chen pa la 'chims nas brgyud pa'i dbu ma'i khrid sogs snar thang pa'i skor dang /
NK129(to)002:2403: gtam shul du mnga' dag gi gdung dang slob brgyud rnams la nyang lugs kyi chos mang po dang /
NK129(to)002:2404: gnas snying bsam gtan sgang pa la chos dbang rin po che'i gter chos sogs mang du gsan cing /
NK129(to)002:2405: mdor na bod du dar ba'i chos la ma gsan
NK129(to)002:2406: pa med pa lta bu yod kyang bdag gi ni
NK129(to)002:2408: de nas gra thang du zha lu lo ts+aa ba'i drung du byon /
NK129(to)002:2410: gsang 'dus rim lnga'i khrid zhu gsung pa la /
NK129(to)002:2411: rim lnga zhus pas rlung lnga'i kha dog so sor gzigs /
NK129(to)002:2412: mnal lam du bzung nas zhing khams mang po bsgrod /
NK129(to)002:2413: bar srid thogs med du gzigs /
NK129(to)002:2414: slob ma dang yon bdag dam tshig gtsang ma rnams
NK129(to)002:2415: kyi bde dog mkhyen pa'i mngon par shes pa mnga'
NK129(to)002:2416: ba sogs yon tan du ma byung bas /
NK129(to)002:2417: sna 'ga' gsung pa la brten nas yul mi kun
NK129(to)002:2418: gyis kyang bsnyen bkur dang 'bul ba rgya chen byas
NK129(to)002:2419: zhing / thugs dam rtags pa zhu ba mang bas
NK129(to)002:2420: g.yengs pa la thugs bsun zhing tshe gcig sangs rgyas
NK129(to)002:2421: grub par dgongs nas bya bral la zhugs te /
NK129(to)002:2422: mon yul du bros nas 'tsho ba ngan ngon la brten te tshe dang sgrub pa mnyam pa dang /
NK129(to)002:2423: snod ldan gyi slob ma byung na chos kyi sbyin pa lhug par stsol bar dam bca' mdzad /
NK129(to)002:2424: mkhar chur le bdun sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK129(to)002:2425: zha lu lo ts+aa ba la sku'i tshe'i bar chad
NK129(to)002:2426: drug cu rtsa gcig gi dgung steng du 'dug pa
NK129(to)002:2427: de / nyid kyis phur pa'i bsnyen sgrub mdzad na
NK129(to)002:2428: slar sum cu'i bar phyir nur te dgung lo dgu
NK129(to)002:2429: bcu rtsa gcig bzhugs par 'gyur zhes /
NK129(to)002:2430: re ma ti'i lung bstan byung ba la de'i nang
NK129(to)002:2431: par rang dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas zla ba dgu sgrub
NK129(to)002:2432: pa la bzhugs de dus bsnyen phur gyi zhal nas
NK129(to)002:2433: me stag phro phro byung ba dang /
NK129(to)002:2434: nga la dgra zhig yod na bsgral chog pa la dgra med dgongs pa byung /
NK129(to)002:2435: yang sgu chul phyug po la bsod snyoms kyis nas
NK129(to)002:2436: bcol ba ma sprad pa' khar bla ma la dug
NK129(to)002:2437: btang / yon bdag kun dang phra ma bcug pa
NK129(to)002:2438: de thugs kyi dran pas phur pa ldeg ldeg pa
NK129(to)002:2440: du ba sngo phyur phyur byung /
NK129(to)002:2441: der nga'i bla ma'i sku tshe mthud yod dam /
NK129(to)002:2442: phur pa ni grub byung dgongs nas /
NK129(to)002:2443: thug rdor gyi phag sha skam po tshal pa gcig yod pa de tshogs 'khor byas /
NK129(to)002:2444: gtor ma rgyas par bsngosa nas mnal lam brtags pas /
NK129(to)002:2445: dkyil 'khor gyis nang nas yin bsam pa la /
NK129(to)002:2446: yang res sgrub khang nas yin bsam pa'i bud med
NK129(to)002:2447: rta pa mang pos shing gi phur pa dkar po
NK129(to)002:2448: dang / grod pa mang po khur byung nas sgu
NK129(to)002:2449: chul gzhis sgar song nas grod pa nas khrag mang
NK129(to)002:2451: de nas zha lu lo ts+aa ba'i drung du byon
NK129(to)002:2452: tsa na 'bul ba cang med nas sku 'phrag nyul
NK129(to)002:2453: bas / a ru ra rlon pa sum cu so gcig byung ba bla ma la phul bas /
NK129(to)002:2454: shin tu dgyes te phyag tu bzhes /
NK129(to)002:2455: gcig tshul gnang nas rang gi khar bcug pa rmis /
NK129(to)002:2457: bla ma'i sku tshe mthud 'dug ste /
NK129(to)002:2458: nga la gcig gnang ba des lo gcig gis nyung ngu song pa 'dra snyam pa byung ste /
NK129(to)002:2459: phyis de ka ltar byung ste dgung lo dgu cu bzhugs pa yin /
NK129(to)002:2460: de nas zla ba gcig tsam nas sgu chul ba
NK129(to)002:2461: tsho la bshal rims byung nas rang re la sems
NK129(to)002:2462: gnag tshad shi / dug gtong mi phyug po tshang gi grong rkang stong /
NK129(to)002:2463: phur pa 'dis nga'i bla ma'i sku tshe mthud te /
NK129(to)002:2464: nga ngan song du de'u skyur /
NK129(to)002:2469: gtsug tor dri ma med rnams kyis sgrib sbyong la lo re re ste lo lnga mtshams bsdams /
NK129(to)002:2470: mi che chung lnga bcu tsam shi ba 'drong e yod yin te skyon che gsungs /
NK129(to)002:2471: spyir bla ma 'dis mkhas btsun bzang gsum dang /
NK129(to)002:2473: thos bsam sgom gsum la thugs rtsol mdzad lugs sogs
NK129(to)002:2474: ni sems can gyi blor shong ba dka' zhing yon
NK129(to)002:2475: tan de dag gi cha shas tsam yang bdag lta
NK129(to)002:2476: bus brjod par mi nus la /
NK129(to)002:2477: rnam thar mdo tsam zhig 'bri bar zhus pas ma gnang /
NK129(to)002:2478: phag tu zin bris btab pa gcig yod pa de yang mngon shes kyis dgongs nas longs shog gsungs /
NK129(to)002:2480: khyod rang dang dad pa che ste /
NK129(to)002:2481: dus ngan gyis sems can tsho sdig pa sogs lugs 'dis chog pa 'dug pa la /
NK129(to)002:2482: nga la bsten nas sdig pa 'theb bsog tu ma 'jug /
NK129(to)002:2483: ma dad pa skye na sdug ge tsho dmyal bar skye /
NK129(to)002:2484: nga la yon tan yod tshul su la yang ma lab gsung nas zin bris me la btab /
NK129(to)002:2485: bka' rgya dam pas brjod du yang med lags /
NK129(to)002:2486: phyis sku thim par nye ba na /
NK129(to)002:2487: da lo'i 'brum nad 'di la nga thag ring gcig la bros 'gro gsung nas /
NK129(to)002:2488: skabs shig gar song cha med du song /
NK129(to)002:2489: de nas me tog gi char dang /
NK129(to)002:2491: sa g.yo ba dang nyi ma bdun btud mar byung /
NK129(to)002:2492: shar phyogs su sgra chen po grags pa sogs kyi ltas la bsten nas /
NK129(to)002:2493: slob ma re re gnyis dang yon bdag chos nyams
NK129(to)002:2494: ldan pa dag ni sku ma spangs bar mkha' spyod
NK129(to)002:2495: du gshegs sam zhes zer ro //
NK129(to)002:2496: de ltar yongs 'dzin dam pa 'di dgung lo ji tsam bzhes zhes zhus pa na /
NK129(to)002:2497: brgyad cu rtsa lnga tsam a mi lon /
NK129(to)002:2498: da rgas nas brjed te mi mnga' zhes thams cad la gsung pa zhig yin mod kyis /
NK129(to)002:2501: dmar ston sogs kyi drung du chos gsan pa dang /
NK129(to)002:2502: thog mtshungs pa yin pas mi yul du lo nyis brgya lhag tsam bzhugs pa 'dra zhing /
NK129(to)002:2503: yon tan gzhan rnams smra ru med kyang /
NK129(to)002:2504: rdo rje phur pa la rten nas dngos grub mnyes
NK129(to)002:2505: tshul phur pa brgyud pa'i lo rgyus 'dir med na
NK129(to)002:2506: mi rung bas / cung zad bris pa la dpal
NK129(to)002:2507: ldan bla ma rdo rje 'dzin rgyal mkha' 'gro'i tshogs
NK129(to)002:2508: dang bcas pas snang ba stsal te /
NK129(to)002:2509: bdag gi lam dang dngos grub kyi gegs su mi 'gyur bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK129(to)002:2510: de ltar lha mchog phur pa'i gor bzhugs pas //
NK129(to)002:2511: rigs 'dzin grub thob rim pa byon pa'i tshul //
NK129(to)002:2512: rgya bal bod du bgrangs kyi mi langs la /
NK129(to)002:2513: sngon byung lo rgyus ji bzhin 'chad nus pa'i //
NK129(to)002:2514: blo gros spobs pa bdag la ma mchis mod //
NK129(to)002:2515: de lta na yang rang gis thos pa tsam //
NK129(to)002:2516: yi ge'i lam du gsal bar ma byas na /
NK129(to)002:2517: deng sang brgyud gzhung mkhyen pa smos ci dgos //
NK129(to)002:2518: gtam tsam rna bar sgrog pa mi snang bas //
NK129(to)002:2519: nub par 'phangs nas dge ba'i sems kyis bkod //
NK129(to)002:2520: nongs na bla ma lha la bzod par gsol //
NK129(to)002:2521: e ma rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che //
NK129(to)002:2522: sngon chad bod 'dir dar la rgya che zhing //
NK129(to)002:2523: bstan 'dzin mkhas grub tshad mar gyur pa dang //
NK129(to)002:2524: nyams len mdzad pa'i gang zag bsam mi khyab //
NK129(to)002:2525: deng sang dus na nam langs skar ma bzhin //
NK129(to)002:2526: bstan la phan pa thams cad zhing gzhan gshegs //
NK129(to)002:2527: gsang sngags 'dzin pa 'dod pa 'ga' zhig kyang //
NK129(to)002:2528: 'phral dgos za chog slob par mi nus na //
NK129(to)002:2529: rgya chen rgyud 'grel lag len lta ci smos //
NK129(to)002:2530: ming dang rtags tsam 'dzin pa nyid du gyur //
NK129(to)002:2531: 'di man thos bsam sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i blo med cing //
NK129(to)002:2532: bsnyen sgrub mtha' ru 'don pa'i 'dun pa bral //
NK129(to)002:2533: bzang rdzu 'ug pa sbos ltar 'gyings ba yi //
NK129(to)002:2534: gang zag mthong bas rang sems lhag par skyo //
NK129(to)002:2535: phyi tshul bzang po'i gos kyis rnams spud cing /
NK129(to)002:2536: nang du khyim pa'i sems dang mi 'bral la //
NK129(to)002:2537: bstan dang 'gro ba'i don la rgyab kyis phyogs //
NK129(to)002:2538: 'di 'dra'i bstan 'dzin mthong tshe snying nas skyo //
NK129(to)002:2539: 'dzum pa'i zhal nas bstan pa spel zhes lo //
NK129(to)002:2540: kha bgrad mig btsum sems can snying rje skad //
NK129(to)002:2541: zhe nas lag len rang gi rnyed bkur sgrub //
NK129(to)002:2542: bstan 'gro'i bya ba bshol 'di snying nas skyo //
NK129(to)002:2543: mang pos bkur ba'i zas nor gyis ci bya //
NK129(to)002:2544: rang gi sems la rang gi mi khrel ba'i //
NK129(to)002:2545: slob gnyer bsnyen bsgrub lam rtags thon tsam re //
NK129(to)002:2546: med na rang gi rang la ma bslus sam //
NK129(to)002:2547: bdag ni 'dod pa'i lha yi bdud dbang gis //
NK129(to)002:2548: nyin mtshan dal med grong chog bon ltar rgyug /
NK129(to)002:2549: dkor gyi phung pos shes rgyud sgrib pas non //
NK129(to)002:2550: yon tan gsar du skye ba lta ci zhig /
NK129(to)002:2551: sngar shes skyabs 'gro tsam yang brjed de thal //
NK129(to)002:2552: dal 'byor don med rnam g.yeng dbang du song //
NK129(to)002:2554: da ni dben par don gnyis sgrub par smon //
NK129(to)002:2555: 'di ltar snod bcud nyams pa'i dus dbang gis //
NK129(to)002:2556: sangs rgyas bstan dang skye dgu'i bde skyid nyams //
NK129(to)002:2557: rang dang gzhan gyis spyod tshul mtha' dag la //
NK129(to)002:2558: bsam bzhin bsam bzhin skyo ba gting nas skyes //
NK129(to)002:2559: da ni gzhan skyon sems brjod nyes dmigs che //
NK129(to)002:2560: rang skyon 'don pa dam pa'i spyod pa lags //
NK129(to)002:2561: de'i phyir rang drin rang la che ba'i thabs //
NK129(to)002:2562: legs nyes yin min kha 'khyams mi smra bar //
NK129(to)002:2563: thos bsam sgom gsum brtson pa'i lam zhugs te //
NK129(to)002:2564: ring por mi thog rang btsan zin par smon //
NK129(to)002:2565: rang don bslu ba'i gzhan don ltar snang 'dis //
NK129(to)002:2566: sngar yang don med bya ba du ma byas //
NK129(to)002:2567: da ni sol ba 'bad de mi bkru bar //
NK129(to)002:2568: skal ldan srid na de don byed par smon //
NK129(to)002:2569: yun ring srid par 'gro don brtson pa dang //
NK129(to)002:2570: khyad par dam chos nyams pa de gso ba'i //
NK129(to)002:2571: lugs 'di rgyal sras rnams kyi spyod pa lags //
NK129(to)002:2572: de phyir chos rnams ci nus spel bar smon //
NK129(to)002:2573: des na mdo rgyud man ngag rgya mtsho dang //
NK129(to)002:2574: khyad par lam bzang rdo rje phur pa'i gzhung //
NK129(to)002:2575: ma lus mi nub gsal bar ston nus par //
NK129(to)002:2576: skye ba 'di dang brgyud mar 'gyur ba smon //
NK129(to)002:2577: 'on kyang dman pa bdag 'dra'i spyod tshul gyis //
NK129(to)002:2578: rgya chen lam bzang snang bar ma nus na //
NK129(to)002:2579: de slad rgyal ba rnams kyis thugs rje yis //
NK129(to)002:2580: 'gro kun sngags kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK129(to)002:2581: kun kyang mang du thos pa'i mthar son te //
NK129(to)002:2582: bsam pas don rig bsgoms pas dngos grub thob //
NK129(to)002:2583: rig 'dzin rnam bzhi rim gyiis mngon gyur te //
NK129(to)002:2584: skyobs pa pad+ma rgyal po de mtshungs shog /
NK129(to)002:2585: ma gyur drin can mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK129(to)002:2586: las dang dus kyi sbyor ba las byung ba'i //
NK129(to)002:2587: mi mthun rgud pa mtha' dag nyer zhi nas //
NK129(to)002:2588: bskal pa rdzogs ldan bzhin du bde bar shog /
NK129(to)002:2589: rdo rje phur pa'i chos tshul nyi 'od kyis //
NK129(to)002:2590: bstan dgra mun tshogs mtha' dag drung phyung ste //
NK129(to)002:2591: srid par bdud kyi sbyor ba las gyur pa //
NK129(to)002:2592: chos kyi bar chad ma lus zhi bar shog /
NK129(to)002:2593: rta gdong kun nas tsha ba'i me dang ni //
NK129(to)002:2594: gang+g+aa'i klung dang pak+shu'i rgyun bzhin du //
NK129(to)002:2595: rgyun mi chad pa srid pa ji srid par /
NK129(to)002:2596: dam pa'i chos 'di mi nub dar bar shog /
NK129(to)002:2597: thub dbang bstan pa'i gzhi ma dge 'dun te //
NK129(to)002:2598: de yang bdag rkyen byed la rag lus pas //
NK129(to)002:2599: gang zhig bstan pa mchod pa'i sbyin bdag yang //
NK129(to)002:2600: tshe ring nad med bde skyid ldan par shog /'dis mtshon bdag gis ji srid sangs rgyas bar //
NK129(to)002:2601: dge tshogs ji snyed gang zhig thob 'gyur ba //
NK129(to)002:2602: shel dang zla ba kun+da ltar dkar ba //
NK129(to)002:2603: des ni 'gro 'dis phur pa grub gyur cig //
NK129(to)002:2604: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i chos kyi byung tshul lo
NK129(to)002:2605: rgyus ngo mtshar rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs zhes bya ba
NK129(to)002:2606: / rang dang skal par ldan pa rnams kyi brjed byang du /
NK129(to)002:2607: sh+aakya'i btsun pa nam mkhar spyod pa zhes bya bas
NK129(to)002:2608: sa mo bya'i lo dbos nya'i gang ba dang po'i
NK129(to)002:2609: tshes la rdzogs par sbyar ba 'dis kyang rgyal ba'i
NK129(to)002:2610: bstan pa phyogs dus kun tu rgyas pa dang /
NK129(to)002:2611: 'gro ba rnams bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i dpal la dus kun tu spyod par gyur cig //
